# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:31
translate jp a1_saturday_support_f2d1123c:

    # "The students roll into class for the Saturday morning session, each and every one of them sporting the tired eyes of people who have worked through the night."
    "生徒たちが土曜の朝のホームルームのために教室に集まってくる。みんな夜通し作業をしていたのか、疲れが目に表れている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:33
translate jp a1_saturday_support_420125eb:

    # "With only a day left to prepare, I suppose it's not so surprising. Thankfully, we only have to suffer through classes until the lunch break, and then our time is our own."
    "準備期間は残り一日しかないので、それほど驚くことではないだろう。ありがたいことに、今日の授業は半日しかない。それを耐えきれば、残りの時間は俺たちだけのものだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:38
translate jp a1_saturday_support_9e4b954c:

    # "Mutou lurches into class in a tired stagger. I suppose students aren't the only people here that enjoy their late Friday nights."
    "武藤先生が疲れでふらふらとよろめきながら教室に入ってくる。金曜の夜更かしを満喫しているのは生徒だけではないのだろう。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:40
translate jp a1_saturday_support_5f4aad5d:

    # "Without saying a word, he scrawls some page and question numbers on the board and slumps down at his desk."
    "先生は何も言わずに、黒板にページと設問の番号をいくつか走り書きして、自分の机にドスンと座りこむ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:42
translate jp a1_saturday_support_399787e7:

    # "It's completely atypical behavior for him, but it appears that no one in the class is going to call him out on it."
    "彼らしからぬ振る舞いだけど、クラスの誰もそのことをどうこう言おうとはしない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:51
translate jp a1_saturday_support_eadb91cd:

    # "Wordlessly, the students shuffle their textbooks into position and get to work. Not wanting to break the trend, I do the same."
    "黙ったまま、みな教科書をめくり勉強にかかる。この雰囲気を壊したくないので、俺も同じようにする。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:53
translate jp a1_saturday_support_a869be7f:

    # "Fatigue has made the class antisocial; not a peep is heard among the ruffling papers."
    "疲労でみんなから社交性がなくなっている。紙をパラパラとめくる音以外には、物音一つない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:55
translate jp a1_saturday_support_7d06c4c9:

    # "That can partly be attributed to the two empty seats beside me. For some reason Misha and Shizune aren't present; probably doing council work for the festival."
    "俺の隣の二つの席が空席なのも、その理由の一つだろう。どういうわけか、ミーシャと静音は欠席している。たぶん学園祭関係の、生徒会の仕事だろう。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:57
translate jp a1_saturday_support_afe7193c:

    # "It's very quiet without Misha present."
    "ミーシャがいないととても静かだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:59
translate jp a1_saturday_support_47a4b411:

    # "I wonder if she was born as rowdy as she is, or if she is 'making up' for Shizune's lack of voice."
    "ミーシャは生まれた時から今のようにがさつなんだろうか。それとも静音がしゃべれない分を『埋め合わせて』いるのか。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:66
translate jp a1_saturday_support_dc0c8ac6:

    # mu "Nakai, can I speak to you for a moment?"
    mu "中井、ちょっと話いいか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:68
translate jp a1_saturday_support_413e83ee:

    # "I'm so engrossed in thinking about Misha that I don't even notice Mutou approaching my desk."
    "ミーシャのことで頭がいっぱいになっていて、武藤先生が俺のところに来ていることに気づきもしなかった。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:70
translate jp a1_saturday_support_12be91f2:

    # hi "Sure… what's this about?"
    hi "はい……なんですか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:72
translate jp a1_saturday_support_f53228ed:

    # mu "It's probably better if we speak outside the classroom…"
    mu "教室の外で話すほうがいいかもしれないな……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:79
translate jp a1_saturday_support_dc827ef9:

    # "Something about this doesn't sound too good, but I stand up and follow him out into the hallway."
    "どうやらいい話ではなさそうだ。だけど俺は立ち上がり、武藤先生について廊下に出て行く。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:87
translate jp a1_saturday_support_52bfa7aa:

    # "Mutou stands in the hallway, scratching his head as he works out what he is trying to say. Not knowing what's going on, I wait silently."
    "武藤先生は廊下に立ち、頭をかきながら言いたいことをまとめている。なんなのかわからずに、俺は黙って待つ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:90
translate jp a1_saturday_support_5cd581f5:

    # mu "I heard from the school's head nurse that you had an incident the other day."
    mu "看護師長からこの前のことを聞いたんだが"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:92
translate jp a1_saturday_support_d6dacc57:

    # "Ah. So it's about that."
    "ああ。そのことか。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:94
translate jp a1_saturday_support_4580585e:

    # hi "Well, kind of, but it's not anything to be worried about."
    hi "ええと、まあ、心配するようなことじゃないです"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:99
translate jp a1_saturday_support_b742833e:

    # mu "Yes, yes it is. Anything that can endanger your health is something to be worried about."
    mu "違う。断じて違う。お前の健康を害するものは、それがなんであれ心配すべきことだ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:101
translate jp a1_saturday_support_16f41728:

    # mu "We try our best here to prepare you for life here. Part of that involves knowing your limits, and how to work around them."
    mu "俺たちは、お前がここでの生活に慣れることができるよう最善を尽くしている。そのために、お前の体の限界や、それをどう乗り越えていくかを考えているんだ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:103
translate jp a1_saturday_support_f3fca8d5:

    # mu "It would be remiss of me if I didn't speak up about this."
    mu "このことに関してちゃんと言っておかないと、俺の怠慢だということになる"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:105
translate jp a1_saturday_support_cf0012dc:

    # hi "All right, I get it. I'm sorry."
    hi "ああ、はい。わかりました。ごめんなさい"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:107
translate jp a1_saturday_support_4144580c:

    # "Mutou closes his eyes in frustration, and I realize that this probably wasn't the best thing to say."
    "武藤先生は落胆し目を閉じる。今の言い方は良くなかったかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:109
translate jp a1_saturday_support_e23e9a65:

    # mu "Something tells me that you're not sorry. Pretend as much as you want, but this isn't a normal school."
    mu "どうも反省しているようには聞こえないな。反省したふりをしたいなら好きにすればいいさ。だけどな、ここは普通の学校じゃないんだ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:111
translate jp a1_saturday_support_afb5fef8:

    # mu "A lot of people have put in a lot of time, effort, and money to make sure that you, and every other student here, can have the same level of education as your peers."
    mu "お前を含めた生徒みんなが、同世代の学生と同じ水準の教育を受けられるように、たくさんの人が時間と労力とお金を費やしている"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:113
translate jp a1_saturday_support_da921e3d:

    # mu "For you to abuse that by throwing out advice, especially medical advice, is plain selfish."
    mu "アドバイスを、それも医師のアドバイスを無視して、その全てを無駄遣いするような真似は全くのわがままだ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:115
translate jp a1_saturday_support_0496bfb5:

    # "I'm not quite sure if this is actually how he feels, or if it is some act that he's practiced many times to guilt-trip students into doing the 'right' thing. Either way, it's working."
    "これは武藤先生の本心なのだろうか。それとも、生徒に罪悪感を抱かせ、『正しい』ことをさせるために何度もやってきた演技なのだろうか。どちらにせよ、それは効いている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:117
translate jp a1_saturday_support_22b44716:

    # hi "I understand. This is all new to me, and I apologize. I know my limits now, and I'll be sticking to them."
    hi "わかりました。俺には初めてのことばかりで、すみません。もう自分の限界はわかったし、これからは無理はしません"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:122
translate jp a1_saturday_support_ee80f791:

    # "Mutou appears to lighten up a little, satisfied that his message has been received."
    "俺がちゃんと理解したことに満足して、武藤先生は少し気が楽になったようだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:124
translate jp a1_saturday_support_8a4bdcc9:

    # mu "So, tell me, how are things?"
    mu "で、どうだ？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:126
translate jp a1_saturday_support_419bddc6:

    # hi "Things?"
    hi "どう？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:128
translate jp a1_saturday_support_23a9e4ae:

    # "I expected Mutou to be a little vague, but this is pushing the limits."
    "武藤先生の話はちょっとわかりにくいとは思っていたけど、これは度が過ぎてる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:133
translate jp a1_saturday_support_e3de2095:

    # mu "You know. Things. You've had a week to settle in now, so how are things?"
    mu "ほら、あれだ。もう一週間経って落ちついただろう。で、どうなんだ？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:135
translate jp a1_saturday_support_34195760:

    # hi "Er, fine I guess."
    hi "えーと、順調だと思いますよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:140
translate jp a1_saturday_support_0ad4940c:

    # mu "I see. And how is your… condition?"
    mu "そうか。それとどうなんだ、お前自身の……体調は？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:142
translate jp a1_saturday_support_73a7b639:

    # "The pause before 'condition' seemed a little unnecessary."
    "『体調』という前の間はすこし余計な気がした。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:144
translate jp a1_saturday_support_27be5b31:

    # hi "Haven't had any problems so far."
    hi "今のところは何も問題ないです"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:149
translate jp a1_saturday_support_da530d85:

    # "A brief shimmer of relief passes across Mutou's face."
    "安堵のゆらめきが武藤先生の顔をよぎる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:151
translate jp a1_saturday_support_44dd2e66:

    # mu "Good, that's good. The school nurse was a little concerned that you might have been pushing yourself a bit too hard."
    mu "そうか、それは良かった。ナースが少し心配してたからな。お前は無理しすぎてるんじゃないか、と"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:153
translate jp a1_saturday_support_a652892a:

    # mu "He asked me to keep an eye on you when he couldn't."
    mu "彼の都合が悪いときは、代わりに様子を見ておいてくれと頼まれたんだ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:155
translate jp a1_saturday_support_9e149c74:

    # hi "That makes sense…"
    hi "なるほど……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:160
translate jp a1_saturday_support_b9e2649b:

    # mu "I'd ask that you don't blow us off so freely. As much as we try to give you the level of education that you would get at a normal school, you have to realize that you have limits."
    mu "あまり調子に乗って、羽目を外さないでくれよ。俺たちはお前が普通の学校と同じ水準の教育を受けられるよう努力はしているが、お前の体にも限界があることは自覚してもらわないといけない"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:162
translate jp a1_saturday_support_b304026c:

    # mu "Our goal is to make sure that you know where those limits are, and how to maximize your potential within them. Do you follow me?"
    mu "お前がその限界を理解することと、その中でお前のポテンシャルを最大限に伸ばすことが、俺たちの目標なんだ。わかるか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:164
translate jp a1_saturday_support_fc8f5210:

    # hi "I guess. I mean, I don't plan on doing anything stupid."
    hi "とりあえずは。というか、何も馬鹿なことをするつもりはありません"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:169
translate jp a1_saturday_support_dcf34bfa:

    # mu "Well, that's a start, I guess."
    mu "まあ、最初はそれでいいだろう"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:176
translate jp a1_saturday_support_7e6b8551:

    # mu "So then, onto my next question; how are you finding your studies? I understand you were laid up for a while. We're not too far ahead, are we?"
    mu "じゃあ次の質問だ。勉強のほうはどんな具合だ？　しばらく入院していたのはわかっている。授業はそれほど進みすぎていないよな？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:178
translate jp a1_saturday_support_62c6eb0c:

    # hi "I don't really think so. I tried to keep up when I was in the hospital, so it hasn't been too hard."
    hi "そう思います。入院していたときも勉強してましたし、そんなに大変じゃないです"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:183
translate jp a1_saturday_support_67bb5d64:

    # "Mutou taps his chin and raises an eyebrow as he absorbs this information."
    "先生はそれを聞くと、あごを叩いて眉をつり上げる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:185
translate jp a1_saturday_support_0552bb00:

    # mu "Is that so… I suppose there are still students out there who realize the importance of learning…"
    mu "そうか……学ぶことの大切さを理解している生徒は、まだこの世に存在しているようだな……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:187
translate jp a1_saturday_support_a3bf4a04:

    # "I wouldn't go that far, I was only trying to keep myself occupied in my little life-support prison."
    "それは言いすぎだと思う。俺を生かすためのあのつまらない監獄の中で、暇つぶしをしなければやっていけなかったというだけだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:189
translate jp a1_saturday_support_3f9377e1:

    # hi "Well, yeah. You've got to keep up with these things, right?"
    hi "ええ、まあ。こういうことに遅れないようにしないといけないですから。ですよね？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:194
translate jp a1_saturday_support_bec8d0bf:

    # mu "That's exactly it. One wrong move in this world and you're left behind, right?"
    mu "まさにその通りだ。この世界では一歩間違えると置いていかれてしまう、だろう？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:196
translate jp a1_saturday_support_43ae8568:

    # hi "Er, right. Wouldn't want that to happen."
    hi "えーと、はい。そうはなりたくないです"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:201
translate jp a1_saturday_support_3a48e105:

    # mu "No, no you wouldn't. Every week there's a new scientific discovery. Most of them mean nothing to the layperson, but any one of them could be the key to the Next Big Thing."
    mu "そう、まったくそうだ。毎週、新しい科学的発見がある。そのほとんどは普通の人間にとってなんの意味もない。だがな、そのどれもが次の大発見へのカギとなりうるんだ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:203
translate jp a1_saturday_support_9c0e55ce:

    # hi "I'll keep that in mind…"
    hi "覚えておきます……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:205
translate jp a1_saturday_support_77dda1d6:

    # "It's obvious that Mutou's Serious Talk is over, and he's gone back to his standard, slightly scatterbrained approach to life."
    "武藤先生のまじめな話は終わったようだ。そして、少しおっちょこちょいな、いつもの彼に戻った。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:207
translate jp a1_saturday_support_bf11c025:

    # "I think, in hindsight, that I prefer him this way. He's slightly more predictable in his unpredictability."
    "思い返してみれば、武藤先生はこっちのほうがいいなと思う。普段から予想のつかない人だけど、このほうがまだわかりやすい。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:212
translate jp a1_saturday_support_629a68ae:

    # mu "Well then, I think that's all I really had to say. Let's get back inside, shall we?"
    mu "さて、これで話すことは話したな。中へ戻ろうか"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:214
translate jp a1_saturday_support_22d907c9:

    # "My relief at that suggestion is insurmountable."
    "そう言ってもらえて、心の底から安堵する。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:216
translate jp a1_saturday_support_38b56661:

    # hi "Sure. You're the boss, right?"
    hi "はい、先生。先生のいう通りにします"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:221
translate jp a1_saturday_support_b53ab323:

    # "Mutou pauses for a moment."
    "武藤先生は少しためらう。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:223
translate jp a1_saturday_support_ccbfdabf:

    # mu "I don't think any of my students have ever said that to me before."
    mu "そういう言い方をしてくれた生徒はお前が初めてだよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:225
translate jp a1_saturday_support_0bf1c594:

    # "For an instant I consider replying to this, but something deep within me tells me to shut my mouth and get back into the classroom."
    "一瞬、返事をしようかと考える。でも心の奥底から、黙って教室に戻れという声が聞こえてくる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:234
translate jp a1_saturday_support_741d026a:

    # "A few of the students jump at the sound of the door, rapidly trying to pretend that they are working on the questions on the board."
    "ドアの音を聞いて、生徒が数人びくっとし、急いで黒板の問題に取り組んでいるふりをする。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:238
translate jp a1_saturday_support_d000da35:

    # "Some don't even bother, their heads slumped on the desk as they nap. Thankfully, it would appear that Mutou does not even notice them."
    "気にも留めずに机に突っ伏して寝ているやつらもいる。ありがたいことに、武藤先生はどうやら気がついていないようだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:240
translate jp a1_saturday_support_0e1dc9e4:

    # "He returns to his desk and retrieves a scientific journal from one of the drawers. I guess I got to him there."
    "先生は教卓に戻って、引き出しから科学雑誌を取り出す。さっきの俺との話に影響されたんだろうな。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:242
translate jp a1_saturday_support_d899cd39:

    # "The class returns to the near-silence that Mutou and I left it in before our chat."
    "教室は、武藤先生と俺が話をする前の沈黙に近い状態に戻る。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:244
translate jp a1_saturday_support_879f41fa:

    # "Mixed feelings of tiredness and anticipation buzz around the room. Everyone here is either waiting for a chance to rest or the chance to get their last-minute preparations underway."
    "疲労と期待の入り混じった雰囲気が教室に満ちている。誰もが休みたがっているか、さもなければ最後の準備を進めたがっている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:249
translate jp a1_saturday_support_de5702bf:

    # "The clock on the wall slowly ticks the remaining class time away, until finally the bells cry out, ending the torment."
    "壁の時計が残りの授業時間をゆっくりと刻んでいき、ようやくチャイムが鳴り響く。解放だ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:254
translate jp a1_saturday_support_db47a89e:

    # mu "Before you all leave, I expect the answers for those problems by Monday."
    mu "お前たちが帰る前に言っておくが、回答は月曜までに提出するようにな"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:259
translate jp a1_saturday_support_7685c328:

    # "The class sighs as one, instantly regretting slacking off, but still acutely aware of the more pressing issues at hand."
    "クラス全員がすぐさま怠けたことを後悔し、ため息をつく。それでも、もっと差し迫った問題が目前にあることを敏感に感じてもいる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:261
translate jp a1_saturday_support_a2bee472:

    # "The classroom empties in a blink as everyone rushes to their last-minute festival preparations."
    "学園祭の土壇場の準備にみんな出て行ってしまい、またたく間に教室は空になる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:263
translate jp a1_saturday_support_15f5b046:

    # "I stay behind and try to quickly finish the questions so I don't have to bother with it over the rest of the weekend, with the festival and all tomorrow."
    "俺は残って課題をさっさと終わらせようとする。そうすれば週末の間はそのことを気にせずにすむ。学園祭とか、いろいろあるしな。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:272
translate jp a1_saturday_support_47d5a638:

    # "Apart from me, Hanako is the only one left, obviously waiting for Lilly."
    "俺を除くと、残ってるのは華子だけだ。リリーを待っているのは間違いない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:274
translate jp a1_saturday_support_5bcaefb1:

    # "It's weird that Lilly comes all the way to our classroom to pick her up. I expect that moving around is at least nominally harder for her than it is for Hanako."
    "リリーが華子を迎えにわざわざこの教室まで来るというのも変な話だ。そうやって動き回るのは、少なくとも華子よりリリーのほうが大変なんじゃないだろうか。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:276
translate jp a1_saturday_support_55f6a6dc:

    # "But it's none of my business, and I naturally don't ask about it from Hanako."
    "でも俺には関係ないことだ。当然、華子からそのことを聞いたりはしない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:278
translate jp a1_saturday_support_2d4a461f:

    # "Despite the relative proximity of our seats, neither tries to strike up a conversation about that or anything else either, so an oppressive silence falls upon the classroom."
    "席は近いのに、俺も華子も会話を始めようとはしない。息の詰まるような沈黙が教室を包む。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:280
translate jp a1_saturday_support_f94c2c62:

    # "Time passes in silence. It's probably just fifteen minutes or so but it feels longer. I turn pages of my notebook. Hanako turns pages of the novel she's reading."
    "沈黙のまま時間は過ぎていく。１５分たった程度だろうけど、もっと長く感じる。俺はノートのページをめくり、華子は読んでいる小説のページをめくる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:282
translate jp a1_saturday_support_88725440:

    # "My pencil lead splinters against the paper just when I was about to finish a paragraph."
    "段落一つを終えようとしたところで、鉛筆の芯が筆圧で折れてしまう。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:284
translate jp a1_saturday_support_379b285f:

    # "The sounds of my irritated sigh and subsequent fumbling around for a sharpener feel like they're breaking the mood in the classroom."
    "俺のいらだった溜息と、手探りで鉛筆削りを探す音が、教室の雰囲気を壊しているような気がする。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:286
translate jp a1_saturday_support_1276d8bd:

    # "Hanako keeps her eyes firmly away from my direction."
    "華子はかたくなに俺のほうから目をそらす。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:288
translate jp a1_saturday_support_d67e9142:

    # "Before long, Lilly's tall figure appears in the doorway."
    "やがて、リリーの姿が入り口に現れる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:298
translate jp a1_saturday_support_dc6591cc:

    # li "Hanako?"
    li "華ちゃん？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:305
translate jp a1_saturday_support_4f5e9ecb:

    # "Her name is all it takes to make Hanako jump up from her desk and run to Lilly."
    "名前を呼ばれただけで華子は席から飛び出し、リリーのところまで駆け寄る。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:317
translate jp a1_saturday_support_944b023c:

    # "They talk quietly for a moment, but it isn't long before Lilly leaves down the hall and Hanako idles back into the classroom, taking her seat once again."
    "二人はしばらく静かに話をしていたけど、すぐにリリーは廊下に出て行く。華子はゆっくり教室に戻ってきて、また席に着く。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:326
translate jp a1_saturday_support_13770dae:

    # "I watch Hanako out of the corner of my eye out of sheer curiosity at the idea that the two would be separated."
    "二人が仲たがいでもしたのかと思って、俺は全くの好奇心から、視界の端に華子をとらえる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:328
translate jp a1_saturday_support_c96ed82a:

    # "For a couple of minutes, she does nothing but sit with her chin in her hand, staring at the desk dejectedly."
    "しばらくの間、華子は気落ちしたように机を見つめながら、何もせずに頬杖をついて座っている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:333
translate jp a1_saturday_support_e0b2de0d:

    # "The boredom evidently becomes too much for her though, her slender frame reaching into her bag and pulling out a small book."
    "退屈に耐え切れなくなったらしく、華子のきゃしゃな体はかばんに手を伸ばし、小さな本を取り出す。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:335
translate jp a1_saturday_support_d0f804a0:

    # "Come to think of it, that isn't the one I saw her reading at the library. She must be quite a fast reader to get through them at this rate."
    "そういえば、図書室で見た時に読んでいた本とは違うものだ。この分では、本を読むのがかなり早いに違いない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:343
translate jp a1_saturday_support_22efc459:

    # "After about ten minutes of restlessly shuffling in her seat and trying to read, Hanako closes her book and leaves too."
    "華子は席で本を読もうと落ち着かない様子だったけど、１０分ほどすると本を閉じて、リリーと同じく教室を出て行く。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:345
translate jp a1_saturday_support_002a7fe0:

    # "As should I, since the assignment is all but finished and there is nothing else to do in the classroom."
    "俺も出たほうがいい、宿題はほとんど終わっているし、教室では他にすることもない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:350
translate jp a1_saturday_support_45acb09c:

    # "Not really feeling energetic, I just go straight to my room and read for the rest of the day."
    "あまりやる気が出ない。ただまっすぐ部屋に向かい、一日の残りを本を読んで過ごす。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:374
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_22efc459:

    # "After about ten minutes of restlessly shuffling in her seat and trying to read, Hanako closes her book and leaves too."
    "華子は席で本を読もうと落ち着かない様子だったけど、１０分ほどすると本を閉じて、リリーと同じく教室を出て行く。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:376
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_002a7fe0:

    # "As should I, since the assignment is all but finished and there is nothing else to do in the classroom."
    "俺も出たほうがいい、宿題はほとんど終わっているし、教室では他にすることもない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:378
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_40e8fd1d:

    # "Not that I have anything to do anywhere else either."
    "とはいえ、他の場所ですることがあるわけでもない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:388
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_57620ad4:

    # "The school is a beehive of activity but nobody pays me any heed."
    "校内は活発なミツバチの巣のようだけど、俺に気をとめる者は誰もいない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:390
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_10cdacf5:

    # "I saunter past classrooms filled with students frantically doing this and that, buzzing around like little worker bees."
    "どの教室でも、たくさんの生徒たちが働きバチのようにうるさくおしゃべりしながら、いろいろな作業に夢中になっている。俺はそれを横目にみながら、ぶらぶらと散歩する。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:392
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_78ab902c:

    # "You wouldn't guess the school day is over."
    "まるでまだ放課後じゃないみたいだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:402
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_35eb06ec:

    # "It's a bit quieter outside, but not by much."
    "外はもう少し静かだけど、でもそれほどじゃない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:404
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_fcac7ce7:

    # "People zip by, left and right, hurrying as quickly as they can; busy and energetic."
    "みんなとにかく急ぎ足で、右へ左へと駆けていく。忙しくて、活気がある。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:406
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_b8bcfc85:

    # "I feel the opposite. The midday sun seems to be draining all the spirit out of my body, making it feel limp all over."
    "俺の気分は正反対だ。真昼の日差しが俺の体から気力を全部吸い取っているみたいだ。おかげで全身がだるい。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:408
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_cfb1cfd4:

    # "Warm, soft air flows inside my shirt, feeling like a cushion."
    "俺のシャツの中を流れていく暖かく柔らかな風は、まるでクッションのようだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:410
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_867145d0:

    # "I yawn lazily, thinking about what I'd do."
    "俺は気だるいあくびをしながら、何をしようか考える。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:412
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_1efb7854:

    # "I'll drop off my books at the dorms first, and then… something I haven't decided yet."
    "まずは本を寮に置いてこよう。それからは……まだ何も決めていない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:414
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_44f7f200:

    # "Maybe Kenji is in his room."
    "健二は部屋にいるかもな。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:421
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_621e5f88:

    # "On the way to dorms, I spot Emi coming my way, running despite not having those weird running prosthetics on. I wave at her and she skids to a stop."
    "寮に戻る途中、向こうから笑美がやってくるのを見かける。あの奇妙なランニング用の義足はつけていないけど、走ってやってくる。俺が手を振ると、笑美は横滑りしながら足を止める。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:429
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_f8e91059:

    # emi "Yo, Hisao!"
    emi "やっほー、久夫くん！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:431
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_880c5197:

    # "Spatters of white and green paint adorn her nose and chin respectively, but her smile is wide, as it seems it always is."
    "鼻には白の、あごには緑のペンキが跳ねているけど、笑美はいつも通りに満面の笑みを見せる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:436
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_1540a895:

    # "She leans closer to me, amplifying the feeling she is examining me."
    "笑美は俺に身を寄せ、こちらを問いただすような雰囲気を強める。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:438
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_9fd8abef:

    # emi "Whatchadoin'?"
    emi "なにしてんのっ？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:440
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_865194e4:

    # hi "Nothing, really. I don't have anything to do for the festival and everyone else seems to be doing something important."
    hi "別に何も。学園祭で何もすることがなくて。他のみんなは重要そうなことやってるみたいだし"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:445
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_9c187217:

    # emi "That's perfect! Then you can help me and Rin!"
    emi "完璧！　それなら、あたしと琳を手伝ってよ！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:447
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_40461049:

    # hi "With the festival preparations? Eeeh, I'm not sure if I would be of much help."
    hi "学園祭の準備か？　うーん、そんなに役に立てるかどうかわからないけど"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:452
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_10b4f477:

    # emi "That's fine! I'm not much help either!"
    emi "大丈夫！　あたしもそんなに役に立ってないからさ！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:454
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_b98389fc:

    # "Emi grabs my wrist and starts dragging me back inside the school quite forcefully."
    "笑美は俺の手首をつかむと、むりやり俺を学校に引きずり戻そうとする。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:462
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_410693c7:

    # "Even her walking speed is more like jogging, making me stumble over myself simply trying to keep up."
    "笑美が歩く速度はむしろジョギングに近く、それについていくだけでも俺の足はもつれる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:467
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_e65b0150:

    # "The stairs slow Emi down a little bit. Maybe it's hard to climb with her legs, or maybe she's finally run out of breath."
    "階段では笑美は少し速度を落とす。彼女の足では登りづらいのだろう。あるいは、笑美もとうとう息を切らしたか。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:475
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_bd6aacd5:

    # "We go all the way back to the third floor and to the seniors' hallway, ending up where I left five minutes ago. I could just as well have stayed here waiting for Emi, had I known."
    "結局俺たちははるばる３階まで戻り、５分前に出た３年生の教室のある廊下にたどり着く。笑美が来るのがわかっていれば、ここで待っていたほうがまだ良かっただろう。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:477
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_fd58e088:

    # hi "So are you… is Rin working on that mural, still?"
    hi "それで……琳はまだ壁画を描いてるのか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:482
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_fdc08346:

    # emi "That's right! She needs all kinds of paints and brushes and stuff, so I went to get them from the art classroom."
    emi "うん！　いろんなペンキとかブラシとか材料が要るんだって。それであたし、美術室に取りに来たの"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:484
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_a1e32d78:

    # hi "And you need me to help with that."
    hi "で、その手伝いに俺が要るってわけだ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:489
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_55071bfc:

    # emi "Well… Rin told me you had already helped her so I thought you wouldn't mind."
    emi "うん……琳が、久夫くんが前に手伝ってくれたって言ってたから、また手伝ってくれるかなーと思って"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:491
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_e1f8a5e6:

    # hi "I see."
    hi "なるほどな"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:500
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_d5c06a67:

    # "So thanks to Emi's flaky logic, here I am again, collecting stuff from the art classroom for other people. "
    "で、笑美のおかしな理屈のおかげで、俺はまた美術室に来て、他人のために材料を集めて回ってるわけだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:502
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_45df3b99:

    # "The room is empty apart from ourselves and the lonely specks of dust floating in the air. Emi skips straight away to the back wall, digging out a tiny, crumpled piece of paper from her pocket."
    "美術室は俺たち以外は誰もおらず、空気中を埃が寂しく漂っている。笑美はすかさず後ろの壁まで跳んでいくと、ポケットから小さな、しわくちゃの紙切れを引っ張り出す。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:504
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_b2f7b41e:

    # "While she tries to make sense of the scrawled handwriting, I take a closer look at the materials lying around here."
    "彼女がそこに殴り書きされた内容を読んでいる間、俺はあたりに散らばっている資材に注目する。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:506
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_9f7b896e:

    # "Dozens of paint cans and bottles are arranged on the shelves in a most unorganized fashion."
    "たくさんのペンキ缶やボトルが乱雑に棚に並べられている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:508
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_886c6713:

    # "Some look like they have been left there for several decades; relics of previous art club generations."
    "そのいくつかはまるでそこに何十年も放置されていたかのように見える。前の世代の美術部の遺物のように。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:510
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_ea6d58ea:

    # "Next to the heavy stacks of neatly piled drawing paper are boxes full of different-sized brushes and unsorted crayons."
    "ずっしりと積み重ねられた画用紙の束の横には、様々な大きさのブラシと仕分けされていないクレヨンが詰まった箱がある。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:512
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_b3ab6c5e:

    # "The smells of paint, turpentine and fresh paper float in the stale air, mixing in my nostrils to form that unmistakable scent of art."
    "ペンキやテレビン油、新鮮な紙の匂いが淀んだ空気の中を漂い、俺の小鼻の中で混ざり、いかにも美術的な匂いへと変わっていく。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:521
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_41fa82ae:

    # "Emi studies her notes, comparing them to markings on the various paint cans, and passes them to me as she finds the correct matches."
    "笑美はメモ書きを読み解くと、それらを様々なペンキ缶に記されたマークと見比べ、一致したものを見つけ出しては俺に手渡す。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:526
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_696a1aad:

    # "She stretches her neck to look on the topmost shelf, but it's not quite enough."
    "首を伸ばして一番上の棚を見ようとするけど、なかなか届かない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:531
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_41cd3bae:

    # "Her eye level stays below the shelf no matter what she does. Emi gives up and just looks up to the shelf longingly, like a child at a toy store, huffing in annoyance."
    "どうがんばっても、笑美の視線は棚より低いままだ。あきらめた笑美は、おもちゃ屋にいる子供のようにものほしそうに棚を見上げ、腹立たしげに息を吐く。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:535
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_6dc12176:

    # "After a moment of building anger, she starts jumping up and down, apparently trying to speed-read the labels during the fraction of a second she can see them, and catch what she can."
    "怒った笑美は、今度は上下に跳び始めた。どうやら一瞬だけ見えるラベルを素早く読み取って、手に取ろうとしているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:540
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_28bd69e8:

    # "It's no surprise that she fails miserably, and almost manages to bring the entire shelf crashing down."
    "当たり前だけど、まったくうまくいかない。それどころか危うく棚そのものを倒してしまいそうになる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:542
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_26ca76f8:

    # "Now I see why me lending a hand here would be useful."
    "俺が手を貸してやったほうがいいわけがやっとわかった。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:544
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_c5e2287d:

    # hi "Come on, let me do that. You can't jump high enough, and I don't want you to hurt yourself trying."
    hi "ほら、俺がやるよ。そんなに高くは跳べないだろ。それに怪我でもされちゃかなわないし"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:546
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_486bdb64:

    # hi "Also, I'm like twice your height."
    hi "あと俺、君より２倍は背が高いからさ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:551
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_08dc74c3:

    # emi "You are not!"
    emi "そんなことないもん！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:553
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_92767b46:

    # "She turns around, flaring scorn, flushed cheeks and all."
    "笑美は顔を真っ赤にしてすっかり機嫌を損ね、そっぽを向いてしまう。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:555
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_011afea5:

    # hi "Just kidding, just kidding. Anyway, I'll look up there, okay?"
    hi "冗談だよ、冗談。で、そこは俺が見るよ、な？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:560
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_c3da922e:

    # "She glares at me one more time, but can't come up with a retort. With a grudging 'hmph,' turns her back to me."
    "笑美は俺をもう一度にらみ付けるけど、それ以上の反論はできない。むくれたように『ふーん』といって俺に向き直る。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:565
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_88bbc233:

    # "So I begin scrounging around the top shelf for paint while below, Emi crouches to scavenge what she can from the cupboards."
    "そして俺は棚の一番上からペンキを集め始める。その下で、笑美はしゃがみ込んで戸棚から集められるだけのものを集める。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:567
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_0cb6ef45:

    # "I shake my head a little, after double-checking to ensure she can't see me do so."
    "笑美がこちらを見ていないことを確認してから、やれやれと頭を振る。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:569
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_93a179aa:

    # "Emi having a complex about her height was a surprise; I wouldn't have joked about it otherwise."
    "笑美が自分の身長にコンプレックスを抱いている、というのは驚きだった。知っていればからかったりなんてしなかったのに。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:571
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_0367e340:

    # "She seems easygoing, but I guess everyone has their weak spots."
    "笑美はおおらかそうだけど、でも弱点は誰にでもあるってことか。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:576
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_e1b1ac35:

    # "Only after we have almost all the items collected and spread out on a desk like a treasure hunter's spoils do I realize that it wasn't necessarily the height jab that got her riled up."
    "材料を大体集め終え、トレジャーハンターの戦利品のように机の上に並べる。そこで俺はようやく、笑美が怒ったのは背が低いことをからかったせいではないのかも、ということに気づく。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:578
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_8af6de4c:

    # "She might not like to be told that she can't do something. Like jump."
    "自分にできないことがある、と言われるのがいやなのかもしれない。たとえばジャンプすることのように。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:580
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_08e11e4f:

    # "But Emi herself seems to have forgotten all about it already. Quick to anger, quick to forgive… is she that type of person?"
    "でも笑美自身はもうすべてを忘れてしまったようだ。怒りっぽいけど、忘れやすい……彼女はそういうタイプなのだろうか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:582
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_54bb8f2e:

    # "At least she doesn't seem to have taken anything to heart, as she chatters away happily while we pick up the rest of the items and then make our way back to Rin."
    "少なくとも、もう気にしてはいないようだ。残りの材料を集めて、琳のところへ戻る間、笑美はずっと楽しそうにおしゃべりを続ける。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:590
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_65973da4:

    # "I chivalrously carry the bulk of the materials as we make our way towards the dormitories."
    "二人で寮に戻る間、俺はレディーファーストの精神を発揮してほとんどの材料を引き受ける。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:595
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_6e5b3f3a:

    # emi "Rin is really stressed about getting her painting done. It's her own fault though; she should've started earlier."
    emi "琳は絵を完成させなきゃって必死なの。悪いのは本人なんだけどさ。もっと早く始めていれば良かったのに"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:597
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_1df86ee1:

    # hi "Is she going to make it?"
    hi "あいつ、完成できそうか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:602
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_14c2e0c9:

    # emi "No idea. It looks good to me, but with Rin, you never know what's going on."
    emi "わかんない。あたしは大丈夫だと思うけど、でも琳がすることは予想がつかないからなあ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:607
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_5de47b40:

    # emi "I found her this morning lying in front of the dorm in fetal position. She hadn't slept all night. I can't believe that the night nurses hadn't found her."
    emi "今朝、琳が寮の前でひざを抱えて横になってたのをあたしが見つけたの。琳、一晩中寝てなかったんだ。夜勤の看護の人が気づかなかったなんて信じられなくて"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:612
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_cb413a6b:

    # emi "And now she's painting again like crazy."
    emi "しかも、それでまた狂ったように絵を描いてる"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:614
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_c0fe4ca8:

    # hi "Yeah, I've… noticed that she comes off as kinda… unhinged. So to speak."
    hi "ああ、確かに琳が……動揺してる、っていうのかな。俺も気づいてはいたけど"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:619
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_5340521b:

    # "Emi giggles at that, as well as at my likely too-obvious awkwardness."
    "笑美はその言葉と、明らかに気まずそうな俺の態度にクスクス笑う。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:624
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_8953a2d5:

    # emi "I don't mind it. She's just a little weird sometimes."
    emi "あたしは気にしてないよ。琳も、ちょっと変な風になることがあるってだけだもんね"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:626
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_cddab4eb:

    # "On that I can agree with her. Unlike me, Emi seems to be cool with Rin's… whatever it is that feels so off about her."
    "それには俺も同意する。でも俺と違って、笑美は琳の……あの余りにズレている部分に対しても冷静でいられるようだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:628
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_3df77618:

    # "Still, they don't feel close like Misha and Shizune do. With them working as a single entity sometimes, it's hard to say where one ends and the other begins."
    "でもこっちの二人からは、ミーシャと静音のような距離の近さは感じない。あの二人が一体となったように何かに取り組むのを見ていると、どこからが静音でどこからがミーシャなのか、判断するのは難しい。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:630
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_461c7257:

    # "Even though they're so different, just like Emi and Rin are."
    "あの二人は似ても似つかないというのに。笑美や琳と同じように。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:632
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_a1dea9ea:

    # "And Rin is the most different of them all, different from anyone else I've met."
    "そして琳は他の誰よりも、俺が今まで出会った誰よりも異なっている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:634
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_9bd95d9e:

    # hi "Yeah, I guess she's a very… unique person."
    hi "ああ、あいつはともかく……個性的なやつだよな"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:636
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_63627c92:

    # "I return to that word again, as if it encompasses Rin's personality by itself, but really it's just a substitute for a lengthy description of her oddities."
    "俺はもう一度『個性的』という言葉を使う。その一言で琳の性格を言い表せるかのように。だけど実際には、琳の奇妙さについての長ったらしい説明を言い換えているだけだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:641
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_593fabaf:

    # "Emi giggles as I grasp about for a properly descriptive word."
    "俺が適切な言いかたを探していると、笑美はくつくつと笑う。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:646
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_e07c36b4:

    # emi "She's just weird."
    emi "とにかく、変わってるよね"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:651
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_9255c9d1:

    # emi "You know, earlier, she just spent half an hour sitting on her box."
    emi "ところで、さっきね、琳、箱の上に３０分もずっと座ってたんだ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:653
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_f6a096a7:

    # emi "And stared at her toes."
    emi "それで、ずっとつま先を見てるだけなんだよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:658
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_985b95fc:

    # "She giggles again in a way that makes me think she doesn't know what's funny about it, it just is."
    "彼女はもう一度クスリと笑う。何が面白いのかわからないけど、とにかくおかしい、そう思わせる笑い方だ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:665
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_efb9222e:

    # emi "All that time."
    emi "ずっとだよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:674
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_2c898b2c:

    # "The working area is a mess, but the mural itself has taken over even more of the wall since I last saw it."
    "作業場はひどい散らかりようだけど、壁画自体は前回見たときよりもさらに広く壁に描かれている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:676
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_c594d8b8:

    # "The disfigured human figures have been mostly colored in tones of red, pink, and orange; weird, imaginary… things populating the spaces between."
    "醜く捻じ曲げられた人の形が赤、ピンク、そしてオレンジを基調にして彩色されている。奇妙で、空想的な……何か、がその隙間を埋めている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:678
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_229fba95:

    # "It looks… nice. I can't think of any word that would describe the work concisely and comprehensively so I settle myself on a nondescript 'nice.'"
    "これは……良いものだ。他に一言でこの絵を表現しきる言葉は思い浮かばない。だから俺は『良い』という差し障りのないところに落ち着く。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:680
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_bc131335:

    # "But honestly, it seems that the area around the wall becomes untidier at the same rate as the mural progresses."
    "でも正直、この壁の周りは壁画の進み具合と同じペースでどんどん散らかっているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:682
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_699c259c:

    # "The ground is littered with dozens of paint cans, various art supplies and empty soda bottles."
    "地面にはたくさんのペンキ缶や様々な美術用具、そして空のソーダの瓶が転がっている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:687
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_a0db0cd0:

    # "Rin herself is in the center of this chaos, standing there looking very cozy as if she was a natural part of the scene."
    "当の琳はこの混沌のど真ん中で、自身がその一部分であるかのように、とても居心地良さそうに突っ立っている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:689
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_0ab63367:

    # "Her pant legs have been rolled up to her knees, exposing her thin legs which sport a drying spectrum of war paintings, similar to those on Emi's face."
    "ズボンのすそはひざまでまくり上げられ、細い脚があらわになっている。笑美の顔と同じく、ネイティブアメリカンの出陣化粧みたいに色とりどりのペンキがかかっている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:699
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_95add354:

    # "Emi sprints to Rin ahead of me and gleefully jumps in front of her."
    "笑美は俺を置いて琳の元へ駆け寄ると、その正面に元気よく跳びこんでみせる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:704
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_ae8a1829:

    # emi "I'm back!"
    emi "ただいま！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:709
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_78b1fd61:

    # rin "That was fast. Did you run in the corridors again?"
    rin "早かったね。また廊下、走ったの？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:714
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_40b97f12:

    # emi "Hisao helped me."
    emi "久夫くんが手伝ってくれたの"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:719
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_9a61febd:

    # "Emi points victoriously at me."
    "笑美は勝ち誇ったように俺を指差す。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:724
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_e7d2b194:

    # "Rin turns around following Emi's finger with her eyes, looking at my general direction."
    "琳は笑美の指がさすほうを目で追って振り向き、俺のいる方向を見る。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:729
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_7602cc06:

    # "She nods absentmindedly at me. She looks like she hasn't slept since last night: a vacant, glazed stare that's focused slightly off me, and movements like in a slow-motion movie."
    "彼女はぼんやりと俺にうなずきかける。夕べから眠っていないようだ。うつろで生気のない視線は、俺を見ているようで少しずれている。目の動きもスローモーションの動画のようだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:731
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_3aabe58f:

    # rin "Hello, Hisao. Thank you for the help."
    rin "やあ、久夫。手伝ってくれてありがと"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:733
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_9fb05ece:

    # hi "Don't mention it."
    hi "礼なんていいよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:738
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_5fcec655:

    # rin "I just did."
    rin "もう言っちゃったよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:740
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_edc7b9f4:

    # hi "Never mind."
    hi "気にするなよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:742
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_73968cd9:

    # hi "Looks like you've made progress. Looking good, as far as I can tell."
    hi "進んでるみたいだな。見た感じ、良く描けてるよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:747
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_b596cb75:

    # rin "But now you get more bad luck."
    rin "でもそんなこと言うともっと不幸になるよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:749
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_d9a28fda:

    # hi "I know, but I'm willing to take the risk."
    hi "わかってる。それでも俺は構わないよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:754
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_eb3cace7:

    # rin "That's a very nice thing to say. For me, of course. Not for you."
    rin "へー、良いこと言うじゃん。もちろん私にとってだけど。君じゃなくてね"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:759
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_8a01aec2:

    # rin "This is why artists are always unlucky. They have to constantly look at their unfinished paintings."
    rin "芸術家はいつも不運に見舞われてるんだよ。四六時中、自分の描きかけの絵を見てないといけないんだから"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:761
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_1ea99adc:

    # rin "So artists can't find romance, their favorite TV shows are canceled, or they die young because of an unspecified disease. It's a deep and mysterious law of the universe."
    rin "だから芸術家は恋愛もできないし、好きなテレビ番組も打ち切られちゃうし、若いうちに謎の病気で死んじゃう。深くて謎めいた宇宙の法則だよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:766
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_fd024b7d:

    # rin "Unless they are blind."
    rin "盲目でもない限りね"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:768
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_045dfd4d:

    # "She considers this for a while, looking like she's going to fall asleep."
    "琳は眠りに落ちるかのようにしばらくの間考え込む。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:773
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_6d6ec2a2:

    # rin "There is a boy."
    rin "男の子がいてね"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:778
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_5a74f291:

    # rin "At the art club, you see. Blind boy. So he doesn't. See."
    rin "美術部になんだけどね、盲目なんだ。だからさ。見えないの"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:781
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_ab881c95:

    # hi "You already told me."
    hi "それ、前にも話したじゃないか"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:786
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_5892d5b9:

    # "I glance sideways at Emi and she glances back in a way that tells she has heard this one before too."
    "ちらりと脇にいる笑美を見やれば、彼女も俺にこの話は前に聞いたと言いたげな視線を送る。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:788
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_7d152421:

    # "Neither of us says anything to Rin, though, so she continues her monotone soliloquy like an unfunny stand-up comedian."
    "でも、俺も笑美も琳に何も言わない。なので琳はつまらないお笑い芸人のように、モノトーンな独り言を続ける。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:793
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_991b9318:

    # rin "He should become an artist. No bad luck, guaranteed."
    rin "あの子は芸術家になるべきだよ。不運には絶対見舞われないよ。間違いない"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:795
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_eae651e6:

    # rin "Don't you think that would be a good idea?"
    rin "いいアイディアだと思わない？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:800
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_9bc56ac0:

    # hi "That only blind people should become artists? No, not as such."
    hi "目の見えない人しか芸術家になるなって？　そうは思わないよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:802
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:807
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_be828747:

    # rin "You might have a point."
    rin "確かにそうかも"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:812
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_a241bd14:

    # "Abandoning this train of thought, she turns again to consider her work and starts humming a tune that I think I recognize, but can't remember the name of."
    "一連の思索をほっぽり出して、琳は壁画を吟味するためにまた振り向き、鼻歌を歌いだす。その歌は聞いたことがあるような気がするけど、名前までは思い出せない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:817
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_07ee1e52:

    # "Emi arranges the supplies we brought and moves a few paint cans around, trying to bring some organization to the scene."
    "笑美はその場を整理しようと、持ってきた材料を並べ、ペンキ缶を動かす。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:822
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_46845229:

    # rin "Emi, I need the Prussian blue paint."
    rin "笑美、プルシアンブルーのペンキちょうだい"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:827
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_bbc41931:

    # emi "Which one's Prussian blue…"
    emi "プルシアンブルーってどれ……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:829
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_4e08194c:

    # "She is staring helplessly at seven or eight cans, each with a different tone of blue."
    "笑美は７、８個ある、それぞれ濃さの違う青の缶をなすすべもなく見つめる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:834
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_698e3f95:

    # rin "It's the one with Prussian blue paint in it."
    rin "プルシアンブルーが入ってるやつだよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:839
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_027a4fe1:

    # emi "Geez, Rin! You're not helping at all!"
    emi "もう、琳！　それじゃ全然わかんないよ！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:841
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_6414ebba:

    # "I look around as well, even though I don't know what Prussian blue looks like, either. I wonder what blue has to do with Prussia."
    "俺も周りを見渡してみる。でも俺だってプルシアンブルーがどういう色なのか知らない。青とプルシアにいったいどういう関係があるんだろう。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:843
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_e0e49294:

    # "…Or what Prussia even is. The name sounds vaguely familiar, but I can't place it."
    "……というか、そもそも『プルシア』ってなんなんだ。聞いたことがある気がするけど、思い出せない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:845
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_a726dd7f:

    # "While none of the blues looks more Prussian than the others, the small print on the labels is legible enough to determine that none say anything about the contents being Prussian."
    "どの青を見てもほかに比べてプルシアンって感じはしない。でも、缶のラベルに書いてある小さな字を読むと、どれも中身がプルシアンじゃないってことがわかる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:847
translate jp a1_saturday_an_asethetics_12c5110e:

    # hi "There is no Prussian blue here."
    hi "ここにはプルシアンブルーなんてないぞ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:859
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_b2c9ec53:

    # "Emi heaves a sigh."
    "笑美はため息をつく。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:864
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_888d60b5:

    # emi "I guess I have to go back and get some."
    emi "あたしが戻って取ってこないといけないかなあ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:869
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_e11cbb0a:

    # emi "I promised to help with our class project, though, so I'll be back a bit later. Can you manage without it for a few hours?"
    emi "でも、あたしのクラスの企画を手伝うって約束しちゃったんだ。だから戻ってくるのはしばらく後になるの。２、３時間ぐらい、あたしがいなくても大丈夫？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:874
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_0068f244:

    # "Rin nods, and so Emi leaves."
    "琳がうなずくと、笑美は去っていった。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:885
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_35118de2:

    # "I stay because I like watching Rin paint, and because I have nothing better to do."
    "俺は他にできることもないし、琳が絵を描くのを観たかったので、その場にとどまる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:887
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_b2970988:

    # "I sit on a box and pick up today's book from my bag. It's a story about three guys drinking beer for two weeks straight and doing little else."
    "箱の上に座り、かばんから今日の本を取り出す。２週間何もせずに酒を飲み続けている３人の男の物語だ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:894
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_e59f4b9c:

    # "Rin moves from the spot that was in need of the blue and starts slowly working on another."
    "琳は一箇所に青のペンキを塗り終えると、今度は別の箇所へ移動する。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:896
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_a3a6b25e:

    # "Her foot works the brush steadily against the plastered wall. Layers of paint on top of layers of paint. The mural slowly gains more form."
    "琳は黙々としっくいの壁にむかって足を振る。ペンキが重ねて塗られていき、壁画はだんだん形を成していく。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:898
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_10faf600:

    # "I turn the pages at a leisurely pace. In this chapter they are drinking beer at the protagonist's friend's place. In the previous ones it was the protagonist's own apartment."
    "俺はのんびりとページをめくる。この章では、男たちは主人公の友人の家でビールを飲んでいる。これまでは主人公のアパートだった。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:900
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_7e2cc21d:

    # "It's not a page-turner kind of book, a slice of someone's imaginary life that makes me wonder why it had to be written."
    "特に面白いというわけでもない。ある架空の人物の人生の一部分。どうしてこれが書かれなくてはいけなかったのか、不思議で仕方ない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:902
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_6048ee19:

    # "Why indeed. The reason for doing something creative… it's something incomprehensible."
    "一体なぜだろう。何かを創造する理由……想像もつかない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:904
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_a054e41f:

    # "Like why Rin does paintings. It feels like she and Emi are the same, going squarely against their fates as if it's just out of spite."
    "琳が絵を描く理由もそうだ。琳と笑美は、まるで敵討ちのように自分の境遇にまっすぐ立ち向かっている。その意味では二人は同じのような気がする。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:906
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_147ae45a:

    # "Rin even said something like that. 'Do something you can't just because you can.'"
    "実際、琳はそんなことを言っていた。『できないことをやろうとするのは、それが本当はできるから』と。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:908
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_178ca1d4:

    # "Is that what she meant? Is that her reason? It might be Emi's, she comes off as quite a headstrong person."
    "そういう意味だったのか？　それが琳の『理由』か？　笑美の理由かもしれないな。あの子は結構頑固だから。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:910
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_ea065e7f:

    # "Rin doesn't give off that kind of an air. Thinking about it, she doesn't give off any kind of air, or maybe a different kind every time I talk with her."
    "琳からはそういう印象を受けない。考えてみれば、琳からはなんの印象も感じたことがない。というか、話すたびに毎回違った印象を受ける。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:912
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_208c1ebe:

    # "Why did she say what she said? Why does she, or anyone at all paint, or draw, or sculpt, or write?"
    "琳はなぜあんなことを言ったのだろう。なぜ琳、いや人は絵を描き、色を塗り、彫刻を彫り、物語を書くのだろう。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:914
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_978bdb0f:

    # "I've never had much of a creative impulse so I don't think I can really understand it."
    "俺は今まで何かを作りたいという衝動に駆られたことは一度もない。だから俺に理解できるとは思えない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:916
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_8a0dd678:

    # "It makes me feel hollow inside."
    "むなしい気分になる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:918
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_7a9776e2:

    # "What a grim thought. I can't really decide whether it's true or not, either."
    "ぞっとする話だ。それが正しいのかどうか、はっきり判断することもできそうにない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:920
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_b195d049:

    # "Am I content being this way? I can't deny I'm feeling a little bit envious of Rin, but I can't really consider it a flaw of any kind."
    "俺はこれでいいのだろうか？　琳をうらやむ気持ちがあるのは否定できないけど、それが俺の落ち度とは思えない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:922
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_f3e8b803:

    # "I'm myself and she is herself."
    "俺は俺、琳は琳、だ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:924
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_e5d3571d:

    # "Still, I do need to find something. Something that could… make me feel a little less lost about myself, instead of just drowning myself in these books as I did in the hospital."
    "そうは言っても、俺も何か探さなくてはいけない。病院にいたときのように、読書に没頭するんじゃなくて、何か……この気の迷いが少しでもまぎれるようなものを。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:926
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_18656b29:

    # "I can't help but feel disoriented; the new school, lifestyle and people around me contribute heavily to this sensation."
    "戸惑う気持ちを抑えられない。この新しい学校や生活、周囲の人間のおかげで、その感覚はどんどん強まる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:928
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_59b2b6ee:

    # "I'm trying my best to fit into existing social circles, and most of the people I've met have been really nice."
    "俺だって、ここの人たちの中にとけ込もうとがんばっている。それに俺が会った人たちは、みんなといってもいいほどいい人ばかりだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:930
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_11d2a08b:

    # "It still feels like I'm an outsider, though; like I don't belong."
    "それでも、まだ自分がよそ者みたいな気分がする。俺はここにいてはいけないんじゃないか、と。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:934
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_de4f63ed:

    # "I shake the feeling off, realizing that I'm spacing out. I have neither turned a page of the book, nor done anything for Rin."
    "考えを振り払う。つい上の空になってしまった。本もめくっていなければ、琳の手助けもしていない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:936
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_1be273fb:

    # "She is trying to pour some paint from a big can using only her feet, having not bothered to ask me. Or maybe she did, and I didn't hear it."
    "琳は俺に頼みもせず、自分の足で缶からペンキを注ぎ足そうとしている。あるいは頼んだけど俺が聞きそびれたのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:938
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_ae2e5915:

    # "Either way, it looks very unstable."
    "どちらにせよ、ふらついていて危なっかしい。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:946
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_4c640e31:

    # "I quickly jump to help her, as it looks like she's about to spill the entire contents of the can all over the pavement."
    "琳が缶の中身を道端にぶちまけそうになっているのを見て、俺は飛び上がって手を貸す。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:948
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_cf7a9dbb:

    # "I take the can from her feet and pour some in the bowl."
    "俺は琳の足から缶を取り上げ、代わって中身をボウルに注ぎ込む。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:953
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_2c410d8b:

    # "She doesn't say anything, and neither do I. I catch a glimpse of her eyes, looking silently at me from under her unkempt bangs."
    "俺も琳も何も言わない。俺は一瞬、琳のぼさぼさの前髪越しに見上げる視線を感じる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:955
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_3a7b2314:

    # "It's an unreadable expression, a perfect poker face, mixed with a hint of something like a mild surprise."
    "何を思っているのかわからない。完璧なまでのポーカーフェイスだ。でも、驚きのようなものが少しだけ混じっている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:957
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_5620f013:

    # "I wonder what she is thinking. Maybe she is wondering about what I'm thinking. Maybe nothing."
    "何を考えているのだろう。俺が何を考えているのか、だろうか。それとも何も考えていないのか。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:959
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_5525bd9c:

    # hi "A penny for your thoughts."
    hi "お前の考えてることに１セント賭けてやるよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:964
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_c0dc7bda:

    # rin "Do you have any pennies with you?"
    rin "あれ、セントなんて持っているの？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:966
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_42b9c603:

    # hi "I don't think I do."
    hi "いや、持ってない"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:971
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_34a14114:

    # rin "Then I don't think I will tell. I'm not thinking anything either, so you're in luck. Except now I just did."
    rin "じゃあ教えてあげない。私は何も考えてないから、久夫は運がいいよ。ただ今は考えちゃったけど"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:973
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_cf4cd607:

    # "She frowns, looking very unsatisfied."
    "琳は顔をしかめる。とても不満そうだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:975
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_b798ccb4:

    # rin "It's hard to not think about anything. But it's important."
    rin "何も考えないって難しいんだよ。でも大事なことなんだ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:977
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_61ff7fbd:

    # "I'm about to ask why it's important when some old guy walks up to us, looking like he has some business with Rin."
    "なぜ大事なのか訊こうとしたところで、年老いた男が近づいてきた。見たところ琳に用事があるようだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:985
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_d194624c:

    # no_ "Good afternoon. How's it going?"
    no_ "やあ、調子はどうかな？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:997
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_149d2f37:

    # rin "I can make it."
    rin "できます"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:999
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_7de544ee:

    # "Rin doesn't take her eyes off the wall and responds so naturally that I can only assume they know each other."
    "琳は壁から目を離そうとせず、自然なそぶりで答える。そこから、二人が知り合いであることがわかる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1001
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_d9b89713:

    # "I haven't seen the man before, so I naturally wonder who he might be. Maybe a teacher?"
    "この男には会ったことがない。当然、彼は誰なんだろうと思う。ここの先生なのか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1003
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_b011b5ae:

    # "His hair has faded to a silvery gray, so much so that it looks artificially dyed. I hope that's not the case."
    "髪の色は薄れて、銀色っぽい白髪になっている。色の抜け具合から染めているようにも見えるけど、そうでないことを祈ろう。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1005
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_1461be11:

    # "Small round glasses hang on the bridge of his nose, but it appears he's constantly looking over the lenses, rather than through them."
    "小さな丸い眼鏡が鼻にかかっているけど、彼はそのレンズを『通して』というよりは、その『上から』物を見ているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1007
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_12ce570f:

    # "He's studying the mural intently over said glasses."
    "彼は壁画をしげしげとそのレンズ越しに観察する。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1012
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_34bb662a:

    # no_ "Good, good."
    no_ "よし、よし"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1014
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_f42f72ab:

    # no_ "What bold composition you have here!"
    no_ "実に大胆な構図だ！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1016
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_c870dcb3:

    # "He moves to inspect the mural closer, talking to himself about it in a way that makes it obvious he wants us to hear it too."
    "彼は壁画を端から端まで見ながら、明らかに俺たちに聞こえるように独り言を喋り続けた。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1021
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_43d11aee:

    # no_ "Very good, very good indeed…"
    no_ "実にいい、実に……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1023
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_72777834:

    # "I don't really know what to make of it but Rin doesn't seem to care much. She's looking around her working space, the various bowls of different tones scattered all over."
    "どういう意味で『いい』のかはわからないけど、琳は気にしているようではなく、作業場を見回している。そこかしこに、いろんな色のペンキが入ったボウルが散らばっている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1028
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_aa95e2ab:

    # rin "Hisao."
    rin "久夫"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1030
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_34d1d59d:

    # hi "Hmm?"
    hi "ん？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1035
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_51ae856e:

    # rin "A little more of this."
    rin "この色、もう少し"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1037
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_cd154c68:

    # hi "Give me a second."
    hi "ちょっと待っててくれ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1039
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_265cd401:

    # "I pour a 50-50 mix of two paints into the bowl to create more of the same pale pink tone Rin was using to fill up the shape of a man's face."
    "俺は２つのペンキを半々の分量でボウルに注ぐ。琳が壁画の、人の顔を塗るのに使ったような、淡いピンクを目指して。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1041
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_4189a984:

    # "Rin watches me doing so, which makes me feel nervous somehow. Her face is so unassuming that it feels she's just waiting for me to do something wrong."
    "琳は俺の作業を見ている。なんだか緊張するな。琳の表情はとてもおとなしくて、実は俺が何かへまをするのを待ちかまえているんじゃないか、という気分になる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1043
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_bf45219c:

    # "The man turns to reckon me as well, looking surprised as if he noticed my presence only just now."
    "男も驚いたように俺のほうに振り返る。俺がいることにたった今気づいたかのようだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1045
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_a4483936:

    # "…Maybe he did."
    "あるいは、本当にそうなのかも。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1050
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_0749a2a1:

    # no_ "Why, hello there. Who might you be?"
    no_ "おや、こんにちは。どなただったかな？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1052
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_2f3d47b3:

    # hi "Ah, I'm a transfer student to class 3-3. Hisao Nakai. Nice to meet you."
    hi "えっと、３－３に転校してきた中井久夫です。初めまして"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1057
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_5f7af525:

    # no_ "Mutou's class, eh? Well, I won't hold that against you!"
    no_ "武藤先生のクラスか？　それはそれは！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1064
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_bd05cb6f:

    # "He laughs very loudly. Obnoxiously loudly. A few small birds take flight from a nearby tree."
    "彼は大声で笑う。やかましいほどの大声だ。小鳥が木から飛び立っている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1069
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_8643b5d8:

    # no_ "I'm Shinichi Nomiya, the art teacher."
    no_ "私は野宮紳一。担当は美術だ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1071
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_6fc9c977:

    # "So this is the art teacher. In retrospect, should have guessed that much. He even looks like one, as far as first impressions go."
    "この人が美術の教師か。確かに美術教師というような風貌だ。第一印象から察する限りでは。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1076
translate jp a1_saturday_creative_pain_eaeb213f:

    # no "How did you come to end up assisting my protégée?"
    no "それで、どういうわけで我が愛弟子の手伝いをやっとるのかね？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1106
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_f818b963:

    # emi "We need to go get more, then."
    emi "じゃあ、追加でとってこないとね"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1108
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_2923cf9d:

    # "I open my mouth to say that actually, we're not both needed for such a simple task like finding another pot of Prussian Blue, but Emi's already grabbed my arm and started dragging me off."
    "いや、プルシアンブルーのペンキをもう一缶取ってくるだけの簡単な仕事に、わざわざ２人で行くこともないだろう。 そう言おうと口を開くけど、すでに笑美が俺の腕をつかんで引っぱり始めていた。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1113
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_0ed8f781:

    # "I wave to Rin, who doesn't seem to have noticed that the two of us are even leaving."
    "琳に手を振るけど、あいつは俺たちが立ち去っていることにすら感づいてないみたいだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1121
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_70b520bd:

    # "Well, she'll notice when she goes for her Prussian Blue and finds out it's still not there."
    "まあ、プルシアンブルーを探して見当たらなかったらその時気づくだろう。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1129
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_469cd171:

    # "Maybe."
    "たぶん。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1134
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1140
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_ec3023e6:

    # "Probably not, actually."
    "やっぱり気づかないだろうな。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1147
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_bbfa9904:

    # "While I'm busy thinking of how weird Rin is, Emi's been dragging me back to the art classroom."
    "琳はどこまで変なやつなんだと考えるのに忙しい俺をよそに、笑美は俺を美術室へと引っ張っていく。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1149
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_8d342adf:

    # "I feel myself starting to run out of breath."
    "息が切れだしているのを感じる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1151
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_a01442f1:

    # hi "What's the rush?"
    hi "そんなに急がなくてもいいだろ？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1156
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_d5e5048f:

    # emi "Huh?"
    emi "ん？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1158
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_e091b96b:

    # "Emi's giving me an appraising look, as if she's trying to figure something out."
    "何かを見極めようとしているかのように、笑美が俺に値踏みするような視線をよこす。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1160
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_6fb1bb91:

    # hi "It's just that you seem to be in a hurry."
    hi "いや、ずいぶん急いでるみたいだからさ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1162
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_222bb7c0:

    # hi "I'm not sure I can keep up."
    hi "これじゃ体が持たないよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1164
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_f9b39107:

    # "Comprehension dawns on her face."
    "笑美は納得がいった、という顔をする。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1171
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_e6fdf82c:

    # emi "You're not out of breath, are you?"
    emi "まさか久夫くん、もう息切れしちゃったの？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1173
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_9e31a153:

    # "There's almost an accusing playfulness to her tone."
    "笑美がふざけ半分の口調で俺を責め立てる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1175
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_95770cc3:

    # "I'm tempted to deny it, but then I realize that I've been breathing heavy since we stopped."
    "否定したい衝動に駆られるけど、足を止めてからこっち、自分が荒い息をしていることに気づく。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1177
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_a17618e7:

    # "Guess it's kind of obvious."
    "まあ、バレバレだよな。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1179
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_05c60fd3:

    # hi "A little. Not everybody can be in shape, you know."
    hi "ちょっとな。みんながみんな体調万全ってわけにはいかないんだよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1181
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_1d1f556f:

    # hi "Takes all kinds, right?"
    hi "人それぞれだろ？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1186
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_6b760141:

    # "Emi frowns. It's not a particularly good frown."
    "笑美は眉をひそめる。あまり良くない表情だ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1188
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_d0341977:

    # hi "Er, that is…"
    hi "あー、それってつまり……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1190
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_f4188b8a:

    # hi "I should… get in shape?"
    hi "体を鍛えろってこと？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1192
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_4d936721:

    # "Not that I hadn't already decided to try for that."
    "確かにそんな決心はしたけどさ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1194
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_2d240926:

    # "After that flutter on the track I figure there's a real need to get in some sort of running habit."
    "ランニング中に粗動が起きたことで、俺は走る習慣をつけなきゃいけないと本気で感じている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1196
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_79c438a2:

    # "I was, after all, feeling pretty good until I had my false alarm."
    "なんだかんだで、あんな人騒がせなことになるまでは気分良かったし。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1198
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_afc8e688:

    # "Well, actually I wasn't. But it was… fun?"
    "いや、気分が良かったわけじゃなかった。でもあれは……楽しかったのか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1200
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_fc6d61c0:

    # "Meanwhile, my comment seems to have helped Emi come to some sort of a decision."
    "一方で笑美は、俺の言葉を聞いて何か決心したらしかった。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1205
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_fbf96428:

    # emi "Well, that's it, then."
    emi "うん、その通りだよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1212
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_4e860902:

    # "She gives me a serious look."
    "笑美の瞳が真剣になる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1214
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_e1d6388f:

    # emi "You're joining me."
    emi "一緒にやろうよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1216
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_ce617998_1:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1218
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_37f63bc4:

    # hi "I beg your pardon?"
    hi "今なんと？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1223
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_ac5e9169:

    # emi "In the mornings."
    emi "朝にさ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1225
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_319b38a9:

    # emi "You and I are now running partners."
    emi "今からあたしたちランニングパートナーだよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1230
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_5f59f34e:

    # emi "I've got a routine all planned out. In fact…"
    emi "メニューもすっかり考えてあるんだよ。実はね……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1234
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_2b76611f:

    # "She produces a crumpled sheet of paper."
    "くしゃくしゃの紙を取り出す。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1239
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_15371668:

    # emi "I've got it right here with me."
    emi "ちょうど持ってきてるんだ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1243
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_6cb5f889:

    # "I take the sheet of paper and give it a once-over."
    "俺は紙を受け取ってザッと目を通す。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1245
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_c084a1c6:

    # "Times, dates, and laps, all laid out."
    "時間、日付、周回数、すべてが設定されている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1247
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_60f9adaa:

    # "A slow increase from just a few laps a day to…"
    "一日ほんの２、３周からだんだん増えていって……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1249
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_05b66596:

    # "My God, does she expect to have me running marathons?"
    "なんだこれ、俺にマラソンでも走らせるつもりか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1251
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_73181635:

    # "And where did she find the time to get this all together?"
    "それに、これだけの計画をまとめる時間がどこにあったんだ？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1253
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_90f5f18d:

    # "And how long has she been planning this, anyway?"
    "そもそも、いつからこの計画を練ってたんだ？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1255
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_0c1b1134:

    # hi "You've been planning this?"
    hi "これ、前から考えてたのか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1260
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_5e1ddb38:

    # emi "A little."
    emi "少しね"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1265
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_4a356464:

    # emi "But it's really the nurse's idea!"
    emi "でもほんとはナースくんのアイデアなんだよ！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1270
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_bc8e6d98:

    # emi "He told me to keep an eye on you to make sure you exercised like he told you to!"
    emi "久夫くんが言われたとおりに運動するように、ちゃんと見ててくれってナースくんに言われたんだ！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1272
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_a050b85d:

    # "A vast conspiracy?"
    "巨大な陰謀？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1274
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_b582c1a5:

    # "Maybe Kenji's on to something here…"
    "健二は気づいていたのかも……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1276
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_5988a222:

    # hi "This seems a bit much for just 'keeping an eye on me.'"
    hi "『見てる』というにはちょっとやり過ぎじゃないか"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1281
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_72727655:

    # emi "Well, to be honest I've been trying to find a running partner in the mornings for a while now."
    emi "えっと、実はね、ちょっと前から朝練のランニングパートナーを探してたの"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1283
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_0a831413:

    # "My God, Kenji! If you could only see the scheme unfolding!"
    "ああ、健二！　この陰謀が明かされる瞬間をお前が見られたら！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1285
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_0884f584:

    # hi "What do you need a partner for, anyway?"
    hi "そもそも、なんのためにパートナーがいるんだ？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1290
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_6983d98e:

    # emi "It's easier to keep up a workout if you're not the only one doing it."
    emi "自分一人でやるより、練習を続けるのが楽だから"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1292
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_b35d68ce:

    # emi "Isn't that obvious?"
    emi "当たり前でしょ？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1294
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_cf17ace6:

    # emi "You're less likely to quit if someone else is counting on you to be there, right?"
    emi "誰かに頼りにされてたら、そうそう止めようなんて思わないでしょ？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1296
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_02912bcd:

    # hi "I see. And this won't only keep you running, but it'll make sure that I keep running as well."
    hi "なるほど。するとお前だけじゃなくて、俺も確実に走り続けることになるわけだ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1298
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_66855131:

    # hi "Meaning that I'll be obeying the nurse…"
    hi "つまり俺はナースの言葉に従うことになって……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1303
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_1357cbfd:

    # emi "…and I'll be keeping an eye on you just like he asked!"
    emi "……あたしもナースくんの言った通りに久夫くんを見てあげられる！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1308
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_ef7d1de1:

    # emi "You caught on quick, Hisao."
    emi "話が早いね、久夫くん"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1310
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_6fa6ae2b:

    # hi "And if I refuse?"
    hi "いやだって言ったら？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1312
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_d72658ff:

    # "I have no intention of refusing, of course."
    "もちろん断るつもりなんてない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1314
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_951773bc:

    # "But I've got to at least put up a token resistance to such a masterfully executed plan."
    "でもこんなに巧妙な計画には、せめて形だけでも抵抗を見せておかないと。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1319
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_588e9d87:

    # emi "Well, if you refused I'd have to pout."
    emi "そうだなー、そしたらほっぺ膨らませるよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1321
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_5c7b6f12:

    # emi "And you'd have to live with being the guy who made Emi Ibarazaki pout."
    emi "久夫くんは茨崎笑美のほっぺを膨らませた男として生きていかなきゃいけないよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1326
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_831c464d:

    # emi "You don't want that on your conscience, do you?"
    emi "そんな気がとがめること、やだよね？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1331
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_68788b35:

    # "As if to demonstrate, Emi begins pouting."
    "見せつけるように、笑美はほっぺを膨らませ始める。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1333
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_4c0107c6:

    # "It is the most adorable, heart-wrenching thing I've ever seen."
    "こんなに可愛らしく、そして見ていて心の痛むものは今まで見たことがない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1335
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_649fd263:

    # hi "Okay! I'll do it!"
    hi "わかったよ！　わかったから！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1337
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_e3e5bfb3:

    # hi "Just… don't do that!"
    hi "とにかく……それをやめてくれ！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1339
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_0236b9a5:

    # hi "I feel like I just hit a puppy!"
    hi "子犬でもぶったような気分だ！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1344
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_f89b9789:

    # emi "So it's settled, right?"
    emi "じゃあ決まりだね？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1346
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_aed904f3:

    # emi "You're going to be my running partner?"
    emi "ランニングパートナーになってくれるんだね？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1348
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_275dc3b9:

    # emi "Follow the workout?"
    emi "トレーニングこなすよね？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1350
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_30e28706:

    # emi "And the dietary plan?"
    emi "食事プランも？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1352
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_b8751d8f:

    # hi "Dietary plan?"
    hi "食事プラン？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1357
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_1ebfabe0:

    # emi "Yeah, the dietary plan!"
    emi "うん、食事プラン！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1362
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_386ae2cf:

    # emi "You've got to eat healthy if you're going to get in shape, you know!"
    emi "体を鍛えるには、健康な食生活をしないといけないんだよ！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1364
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_f9976e27:

    # "I examine the workout routine closely."
    "トレーニングメニューをよく見てみる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1366
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_2397ae76:

    # hi "I don't see a dietary plan on here."
    hi "食事プランなんて載ってないぞ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1371
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_966a0cb0:

    # emi "Oh right! I forgot to give that to you!"
    emi "あっホントだ！　渡すの忘れてたよ！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1378
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_9b4f3ec2:

    # "Another crumpled sheet of paper is produced and handed over."
    "またしわくちゃの紙を取り出して、渡してくる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1380
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_5570b875:

    # "It's somewhat less detailed."
    "こっちはもう少し大ざっぱな内容だ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1385
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_97f817a3:

    # emi "I had the nurse help me come up with it."
    emi "それ考えるのナースくんに手伝ってもらったんだ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1387
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_07cda82a:

    # "The amount of dedication that the nurse has to keeping me in good health is pretty overwhelming."
    "俺を健康にしておこうというナースの努力の数々には驚かされるな。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1389
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_adfa8964:

    # "I don't know many school nurses who would get one of their students to spy on me, much less help come up with a dietary plan."
    "生徒にスパイ活動をさせるような保健の先生というのもあまり聞いたことがない。食事の計画を一緒に考えるなんてなおさらだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1391
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_ff0147bc:

    # "Then again, I guess I'm not in a normal school."
    "しかし、俺が今いるのは普通の学校じゃないということだろう。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1393
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_c18d100b:

    # "And maybe that's not such a bad thing."
    "それはそんなに悪いことではないのかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1395
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_af02e292:

    # "Then again, this dietary plan seems to cut out just about everything that'll be offered at the festival tomorrow."
    "でもこの食事プランによると、明日の学園祭で買えそうな食べ物はほとんど全部禁止されている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1397
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_e886e7c7:

    # "Hmm."
    "うーん。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1399
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_be6005e4:

    # hi "So when does our running start?"
    hi "それで、ランニングはいつから始めるんだ？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1404
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_c6ee7fc8:

    # emi "After the festival."
    emi "学園祭のあと"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1406
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_497e1ccb:

    # hi "Right after? What if I've had something to eat there? I could get a stomach ache, you know."
    hi "終わってすぐ？　学園祭で俺が何か食べてたらどうする？　腹が痛くなるだろ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1411
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_6eeb088a:

    # emi "I meant the day after the festival."
    emi "学園祭の次の日のことだよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1413
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_7e42a5ee:

    # hi "I knew that."
    hi "わかってるよ、そんなの"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1415
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_b3a93063:

    # "Wasn't there something we were supposed to be doing?"
    "俺たち、何かやることがあったんじゃなかったか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1417
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_60a47ea2:

    # hi "Oh! I guess we should get that paint for Rin, huh?"
    hi "そうだ！　琳にペンキを持って行かないといけないんじゃないか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1422
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_57398a3d:

    # emi "Oh no! It slipped my mind!"
    emi "あっいけない！　忘れてた！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1429
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_453283a8:

    # "By the time we get the paint and get back to the mural, Rin's already wandered off."
    "ペンキを持って壁画のところまで帰る頃には、琳はすでにどこかへ消えていた。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1431
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_2521d867:

    # "Oh well."
    "まあ仕方ない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1433
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_8ff19416:

    # "Emi and I both decide to part ways there, leaving the paint on the ground."
    "笑美と俺はここで別れることにして、ペンキは地面に置いていく。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1435
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_c3a02d94:

    # "Rin'll find it. Whenever she comes back, anyway."
    "琳が見つけるだろう。いつにせよ、とにかく帰って来れば。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1440
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_bf5c6620:

    # "Festival's tomorrow. I'm actually a little excited for it."
    "学園祭は明日だ。実は俺も少し興奮している。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1442
translate jp a1_saturday_proper_exercise_9ca6771c:

    # "At the same time, the week's left me feeling pretty tired, so I read a little and then go to bed."
    "同時に、今日までの間に相当疲れているのも確かだ。少し本を読んでからベッドに潜る。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1455
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_efa70cfd:

    # "But why would Lilly leave her to her own devices? It seems to be quite out of the ordinary, going by Hanako's reaction."
    "だけど、リリーはどうして彼女を置いていったんだろう？　華子の反応からして、いつもと様子が違うようだったけど。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1457
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1459
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_7b6f9cf6:

    # "…Ah, that's right. I think Lilly mentioned something about going into town today before Rin bumped into us."
    "……あ、そうか。琳と俺たちがばったり会う前に、今日は町に行くんだってリリーが話してたっけ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1461
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_5be1e490:

    # "The thought of that walk makes me look outside."
    "あのときの散歩を思い出して、外を見る。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1470
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_538d0688:

    # "The bright sun and occasional people wandering around and enjoying the afternoon make me yearn to get out of school, or at least do something other than sit here."
    "うららかな日差しに、午後のひとときを楽しみながら散歩している人たちがちらほら見える。その光景に、学園から出かけたいという気持ちが強まる。ここに座っているだけじゃなくて、何か別のことをしたい。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1472
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_52c9dce6:

    # "Giving in to one of my worst vices, procrastination, I decide that history is a subject best studied on a Sunday. Or a Monday. Or on any day other than this one."
    "俺は最大の欠点――先送りぐせ――に負け、歴史は日曜に勉強するのが一番だと決める。あるいは月曜。今日以外ならどの日でもいい。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1474
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_b5f8b14e:

    # "I give a grunt as I lever myself out of my seat, briefly debating with myself whether or not to hang out with Kenji."
    "うめき声を上げながら、勢いをつけて椅子から離れる。健二と過ごすべきかどうか、短く自分に問いかける。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1476
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_77ded6b2:

    # "He doesn't strike me as the 'enjoying the nice weather outside with others' kind of person, really. I guess I'll catch up with him later."
    "あいつは『いい天気だから外で皆と楽しむ』タイプの人間じゃない。間違いなく。また後で会えばいいか。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1483
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_92d4add5:

    # "Changing tacks, I briefly entertain the idea of talking with Hanako, but by the time I look at her seat, it's vacant. She must've left for the library."
    "方針を変えて華子と話をしようか、という考えを少しだけ頭の中でもてあそぶ。でも、華子の席を見るとすでに空っぽだった。図書室に向かったに違いない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1492
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_3de2424b:

    # "Following Hanako to the library seems a bit intrusive. There was a reason she left the classroom, after all."
    "華子を追いかけて図書室に行くのは少しおせっかいすぎる。やっぱり、華子が教室を離れる理由はあったわけだし。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1494
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_bc955519:

    # "And that aside, I do want to catch up with Lilly. At the very least, I'd like to thank her for looking out for me despite her other, obviously taxing, duties."
    "それはそれとして、リリーとは話をしておきたい。そして、せめてお礼を言いたい。学級委員としての大変な役目もあったのに、俺の世話をしてくれたんだから。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1496
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_ad87abe6:

    # "I guess I'll walk around town. With any luck, I should be able to find Lilly. The exercise'll do me some good, as well."
    "町を散歩してみようか。運がよければリリーを見つけることができるはずだ。いい運動にもなるだろう。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1503
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_4b012d02:

    # "Walking through the school courtyard to the gate, I give a small nod to a couple of passing classmates, the gesture being returned in kind."
    "門を目指して、学校の中庭を歩いていく。通りがかった数人の同級生に軽く頭を下げると、同じように会釈が返ってくる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1505
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_b86e091a:

    # "Even from here, the shouts of the sports club members can be heard. From the sheer volume of the din, the track must be packed right now."
    "運動部のかけ声がここまで聞こえる。この騒々しさからすると、グラウンドは今、人であふれているに違いない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1507
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_08a3b428:

    # "I remember what Lilly said yesterday about being dropped right into the middle of a busy time for the school."
    "リリーが昨日言っていたことを思い出す。俺は学園祭で忙しい中に放り込まれたのだと。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1509
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_c770b79d:

    # "While I'm trying to get my bearings and catch up on study that I've missed, everyone else is doing normal school activities. The feeling of being a foreigner still hasn't dissipated. At least, not yet."
    "俺が自分の立ち位置を探り、勉強の遅れを取り戻そうとしている間、他のみんなはいつも通りの校内活動をしている。よそ者だという感覚はまだ拭いきれない。少なくとも、今は。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1511
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_b117b1ba:

    # "Well, I guess not everything's bad."
    "まあ、何もかもが嫌ってわけじゃない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1513
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_393fb286:

    # "This is a private school, and that much is easily noticed when walking around outside. Not only are the school grounds huge, but the buildings themselves are immaculate and quite divorced from the dime-a-dozen concrete blocks of public schools."
    "ここが私立学校だということは、外を歩けばすぐにわかる。単に敷地が大きいだけでなく、建物自体が汚れもなく清潔で、公立の安っぽいブロック作りの建物とはかけ離れている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1515
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_a0ee181a:

    # "There's also the fact that there's a much stronger feeling of community here, or at least a friendlier atmosphere. At my old school, it was generally accepted that people would keep to their little clique and be done with it."
    "それに、ここでは人とのより強いつながりも感じる。少なくとも、親しみやすい雰囲気がある。前の学校は、仲間内でグループになっていればいいという感じだった。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1520
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_5b0b42ac:

    # "Eventually I reach the gate, and begin to walk down the road and into town."
    "そうするうちに門にたどり着き、町へ向かって歩き出す。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1525
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_f971a5af:

    # "Well, that was fairly productive."
    "まあ、これは結構有意義だった。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1527
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_36581efd:

    # "Having seen a fair portion of town, even including the houses perched on the hills around the outskirts, I decide to take a walk around the park before heading back."
    "町のかなりの部分、町外れの丘の上にたたずむ家さえも見て回る。帰る前に、公園のまわりを散歩しようと思い立つ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1529
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_3454461e:

    # "Living in the city all my life, the total lack of smartly-dressed businessmen and fashionably-dressed girls strikes me as incredibly unusual."
    "ずっと都会に住んでいたから、こぎれいな服のビジネスマンや、着飾った女の子がまったくいないことにかなりの違和感を感じる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1531
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_46c26816:

    # "All that's to be seen are the odd elderly person shuffling along the sidewalk and assorted busily chatting pairs of middle-aged women outside of small storefronts."
    "目に映るのは、歩道で足を引きずっている風変わりなお年寄りと、小さな店の軒先で熱心に世間話をしているおばさんたちだけだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1535
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_5a1c2e88:

    # "Walking along the road to the park quickly distracts me from them, though, making me realize that I perhaps pushed myself further than I should have done to see as much as I could."
    "公園へ続く道を歩いていると、すぐにその人たちからも気が逸れる。でもそのせいで、周りのものをできるだけ見ようと無理しすぎたかもしれないと気づく。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1537
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_f34dbcfa:

    # "As my breath begins to wheeze and my chest tightens more and more, I give up on the prospect of soldiering on."
    "息がゼイゼイといいだし、胸がますます締めつけられる。これ以上頑張るのはやめよう。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1544
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_c9e94dc6:

    # "After a quick glance around the park as I enter, I take a seat on a wobbly old bench that I notice near a couple of vending machines."
    "公園に入るとざっと辺りを見回し、二台ならんだ自動販売機の近くにある、ぐらつくベンチを見つけて座る。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1546
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_9fba6aee:

    # "For minutes on end I sit with my head bent over, forcing myself to take deep breaths. I feel more like an old man than a teenager who should be in the prime of his life."
    "数分間ずっと座ったままうつむき、無理矢理深呼吸をする。青春真っ盛りの十代というより、老人になった気分だ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1548
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_ccc267ec:

    # "The stay in hospital, the surgery and the medications must be taking their toll on me. Dammit."
    "入院生活や手術、薬物治療のせいに違いない。くそっ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1550
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_5df559fc:

    # "Eventually, my breathing returns to normal and the muscles in my chest loosen, not without a fair measure of relief. I guess this means the end of my little sojourn though, in any case."
    "そうするうちに呼吸は正常になり、胸の筋肉も緩む。俺は少なからずほっとする。とりあえずは、これで一時休憩も終わりというわけだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1557
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_858ce63a:

    # "There's a café on the far corner, so I'll stop by to quench my thirst before heading back."
    "遠くの角に喫茶店がある。じゃあ、のども渇いてるし寄っていくか。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1566
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_61f61f62:

    # "A little bell above the door signals my arrival to an empty counter."
    "ドアの上の小さなベルが鳴り、誰もいないカウンターに俺が来たことを合図する。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1568
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_31e33b7b:

    # "For a few moments I stand there waiting, my eyes every now and again drifting from one end of the counter to the other searching for a service bell."
    "立ったまま、少しの間待つ。時々、カウンターの端から端まで目をぼんやりと動かし、呼び鈴を探す。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1573
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_19dbe6a7:

    # "Eventually a door some ways behind the counter opens, the person emerging from it taking me by complete surprise."
    "そのうちに、カウンターの少し後ろにあるドアが開く。現われた人物に、俺はとても驚いてしまう。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1575
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_c5b72b03:

    # hi "Yu… Yuuko?"
    hi "ゆ……優子さん？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1577
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_d5cc369e:

    # hi "Hi, I had no idea you worked here."
    hi "こんにちは。ここで働いてるなんて知りませんでしたよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1579
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_1aa44168:

    # "I really have no idea how to address her either, given that she is technically school staff as well as, apparently, a waitress."
    "優子さんをどう呼べばいいのか、さっぱりわからない。理屈の上では学園の職員だけど、どうやらここのウェイトレスでもあるようだし。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1584
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_e0da63d0:

    # yu "Ah, yes, um…"
    yu "あー、うん、えっと……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1586
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_c421110c:

    # "She quickly paces up to the counter, before flinging her upper half downwards in an overacted bow."
    "優子さんは急いでカウンターに立ち、上半身を思いきり下に放り出して大げさなおじぎをする。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1591
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_0d16fb85:

    # yu "Welcome to the Shanghai! May I take your order?"
    yu "上海にようこそ！　ご注文はお決まりですか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1593
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_24449d9e:

    # "Straight down to business, I see."
    "いきなり注文とるのか。なるほどな。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1595
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_70b5117c:

    # hi "I don't know… well, some coffee, please?"
    hi "どうしようかな……じゃあ、コーヒーをもらえます？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1600
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_4d23c017:

    # yu "Yes, certainly. I'll make it right away and bring it to you when it's done."
    yu "かしこまりました。すぐにご用意いたします"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1602
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_0baaf27e:

    # hi "Uh, thanks."
    hi "えーと、ありがとうございます"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1604
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_b9389667:

    # "Yuuko's formality takes me aback. She seems to take her job very seriously."
    "優子さんの堅苦しさにはびっくりだ。とても真面目に仕事をしているらしい。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1609
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_64b457e9:

    # "Obeying her instructions, I turn around and quickly glance around for a free table. Considering the café seems to be empty, this is a simple task to accomplish."
    "優子さんに案内されながら、空いているテーブルがないか振り返ってざっと見まわす。他に客はいないわけだし、簡単な話だ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1614
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_c0d54bb8:

    # "As I walk towards a table adjacent to the window, I notice a flash of yellow around one of the table dividers."
    "窓際のテーブルに向かう途中、席の仕切りのそばで黄色の何かが目に飛び込む。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1620
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_aa9d3bf0:

    # "Sure enough, no more than a glance is needed to ascertain that it's a certain Satou at the table. That said, I don't recognize the suited figure across the table from her."
    "思った通りだ。一目見れば、テーブルについているのがリリーだと十分わかる。とは言っても、リリーの向かいに座っているスーツ姿の人には見覚えがない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1622
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_e0cebc4e:

    # "Blonde, fair-skinned and only a little shorter, he… she? I think she, must be a relative."
    "金髪で肌が白く、少し背の低い彼は……彼女か？　彼女だろう。リリーの身内に違いない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1624
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_a14649f1:

    # "Since the two are all but silent as the suited figure takes a swig from a cup of coffee, I decide to greet Lilly. Some part of my coming here was in order to meet her, after all."
    "スーツの人がコーヒーをひと飲みしてから二人とも黙っているので、リリーに声をかけようと決める。そもそも、ここに来たのは彼女に会うためでもあるんだから。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1626
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_4d5294c9:

    # hi "Hi, Lilly."
    hi "やあ、リリー"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1631
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_3f263087:

    # li "…Hisao?"
    li "……久夫さん？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1633
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_cad8aa83:

    # hi "Yeah. Nice to see you again."
    hi "ああ。また会ったね"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1638
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_1ddea612:

    # "The suited girl looks up, noting my uniform with a relaxed smile."
    "スーツの少女は俺を見上げ、穏やかな笑顔で俺の制服に目をやる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1640
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_95d2b83a:

    # aki_ "Know each other?"
    aki_ "知り合い？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1642
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_d156ca01:

    # hi "I… guess."
    hi "た……たぶん"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1644
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_8f5a6769:

    # "It's as good an approximation of our relationship as I can think of."
    "俺とリリーの関係を表すのに、それより正しい言い方は思い浮かばない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1649
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_d8597cfa:

    # li "Hmm… care to take a seat?"
    li "あの……お掛けになりませんか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1651
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_c03dda0e:

    # "She says this to the air beside me, but the message is clear enough and I take a seat beside her."
    "リリーは俺ではなく、その横の空間に向かって言う。でも言いたいことは伝わったので、俺はリリーの横に座る。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1656
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_e56ba342:

    # li "I suppose some introductions might be in order."
    li "紹介しないといけませんね"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1661
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_4b2cd307:

    # li "Hisao, this is Akira Satou, my older sister. Akira, this is Hisao Nakai, another Yamaku student."
    li "久夫さん、こちらは砂藤晃、私の姉です。姉さん、こちらは中井久夫さん。山久学園の学生なの"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1663
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_e1b3be86:

    # "Looks like my guess was correct. The newly-introduced Akira gives a nod, which I return."
    "俺の予想は正しかったようだ。改めて紹介された晃さんは会釈をくれ、俺もそれに答える。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1665
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_e0fc3caf:

    # "What I don't return however, is the almost analytical gaze with which she looks me over."
    "でも、俺を分析するかのような晃さんの視線に、俺は答えない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1674
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_909998ba:

    # "As she does so, Yuuko walks up to the table and carefully places the coffee on the table before bowing and taking her leave."
    "晃さんがそうしているうちに、優子さんがテーブルまで来る。コーヒーを慎重にテーブルに置き、おじぎをして去っていく。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1683
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_d4657df3:

    # "Gently bringing my hand to the side of the cup, I realize that it's already at just the right temperature to drink. After taking a sip, the flavor turns out to be just as good as the temperature."
    "カップの両側にそっと手を触れてみると、すでに飲むのにちょうどいい温度だ。一口飲むと、風味もいいことがわかる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1685
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_5b2f5033:

    # "Yuuko seems a lot better at this than being a librarian."
    "優子さんは、司書よりもこっちのほうが向いているようだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1687
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_24d2179c:

    # "I take a good, long drink before relaxing into the seat."
    "じっくりと飲んでから、椅子にもたれてくつろぐ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1689
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_b1886d9e:

    # "It takes mere seconds for Akira's examination to come to an end. Apparently becoming quickly bored with the activity, she turns to her sister."
    "晃さんの分析はすぐに終わる。どうやらすぐに飽きてしまったらしく、彼女はリリーのほうを向く。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1694
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_841b90db:

    # aki "So, how's school recently?"
    aki "それで、最近学校はどう？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1696
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_a7642060:

    # "It seems Akira is entirely unconcerned with someone she doesn't know at all listening to everything they say."
    "二人の会話を聞いていると、晃さんは知らない人にはまったく無関心らしい。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1698
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_0203da0a:

    # "Not that I mind. Leaving them to their chatting, I sit back and continue drinking the pleasantly aromatic coffee."
    "別に構わないけど。俺は二人の邪魔をせずに身を引き、香りのいいコーヒーをくつろいで飲み続ける。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1704
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_4d1cb5ca:

    # aki "Sounds like it's pretty busy for ya, then."
    aki "話聞いてると、結構忙しいみたいじゃん？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1709
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_e6b5127a:

    # li "At least I'm not cooking your meals after school any more."
    li "もう姉さんのご飯は作らなくてもいいのにね"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1711
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_6d648f14:

    # "As they talk, I slowly realize that I'm entirely unable to gauge Lilly's emotions through her eyes; as I would for any other person."
    "二人が話すにつれて、だんだんわかってきたことがある。目を見てリリーの感情を判断しようとしても、まったくできないということだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1713
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_736a08d9:

    # "It becomes slightly unsettling as I subconsciously focus on that fact."
    "無意識にそのことを思うと、少し居心地が悪くなる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1718
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_1310d164:

    # aki "Whoa, so cold. Weren't ya just cooking for yourself anyway? I only ever got leftovers."
    aki "うわ、冷たいなあ。どうせ自分の分だけ料理してたんじゃないの？　あたしは残り物をもらってただけでさ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1723
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_3b746c5e:

    # li "That's not the point… are you managing to feed yourself, at least?"
    li "そうじゃなくて……ねえ、一人でちゃんと食事できてるの？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1728
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_a5b9bf59:

    # aki "I can cook without blowing myself up, you know."
    aki "当たり前さ。料理してるときに爆発なんてしないよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1733
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_43e66b39:

    # aki "Mostly."
    aki "大体は"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1738
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_8ed0ded5:

    # li "That's…"
    li "それって……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1743
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_1938b341:

    # aki "Hahaha! It's fine, it's fine. I needed to learn sometime anyway."
    aki "ははは！　いいよいいよ。どうせそのうち練習しなきゃいけなかったんだから"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1752
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_fb5e63b3:

    # yu "Ah, Lilly?"
    yu "あの、リリー？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1758
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_53a9fbcc:

    # "Everyone present is momentarily distracted by Yuuko, who places a cup of tea on the table for Lilly."
    "優子さんが来て、そこにいるみんなの気が逸れる。リリーのために１杯の紅茶がテーブルに置かれる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1767
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_639560ab:

    # "Taking the moment to glance at her watch, Akira levers herself off her seat and gives me a quick nod."
    "晃さんは時計をちらりと見て席から勢いよく立ちあがり、俺に会釈をする。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1772
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_35293468:

    # aki "Well, I'd better be off. It was nice talking to ya, Lilly."
    aki "それじゃ、もう行かないと。話せてよかったよ、リリー"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1777
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_51288c0c:

    # li "Akira, do you have to…?"
    li "姉さん、まだいいでしょう……？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1779
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_a04128ab:

    # "Lilly looks genuinely mournful at her sister suddenly leaving. It does seem like she might have the wrong idea."
    "リリーはお姉さんが急に帰ってしまうことを心底悲しんでいるようだ。もう二度と会えないとでも思っているように見える。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1784
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_34bcbe57:

    # aki "Sorry, I need to get back to work. They'll be on my neck again if I don't make it back quickly."
    aki "ごめん、もう仕事に戻らなきゃいけないんだ。さっさと戻らないと、ゴチャゴチャうるさいからさ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1786
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_525f1be1:

    # "So informal… Akira's trim and tidy appearance would give anyone the wrong impression of her."
    "とてもくだけた話し方だ……晃さんのきちんとした身なりからは、誰も想像できないだろう。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1791
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_7182b99c:

    # li "Bye, Akira…"
    li "さよなら、姉さん……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1796
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_68af57e7:

    # aki "C'mon, don't look so down. I'll be around again soon. Seeyas."
    aki "ほら、そんな暗い顔するんじゃないの。またそのうちに来るからさ。じゃあね"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1801
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_dc7dd5f4:

    # "With that, she waltzes out of the Shanghai with her hand held high."
    "そう言って晃さんは片手を高く上げ、上海から軽快に出ていく。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1803
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_f424b8e6:

    # "Lilly still looks pretty depressed, so I try to make some small talk in an effort to take her mind off it."
    "リリーはまだかなり落ち込んでいるようだ。俺はリリーの気を紛らわすために、何かおしゃべりをしようと試みる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1809
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_e678f4c2:

    # hi "She seems nice."
    hi "いいお姉さんみたいだね"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1814
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_b785468c:

    # li "We used to live together, but now that I live at school we hardly ever see each other."
    li "私たち、一緒に暮らしていたんです。でも、今は私が学園に住んでいるのでめったに会えないんですよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1816
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_3c8bef3e:

    # "Despite Lilly having been quite affable, I still don't really know much about her. In hindsight, it's surprising just how much she's extracted from me, really."
    "リリーとはとても話しやすいのに、俺はまだ彼女のことをよく知らない。今考えると、リリーが俺からいろいろ聞き出したことには驚かざるを得ない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1818
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_bcc04ba4:

    # hi "You used to live together? Was it somewhere around here?"
    hi "一緒に住んでたの？　この辺のどこか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1820
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_4b8cfe0a:

    # li "It was pretty far south, so the trip into Yamaku was fairly long."
    li "ずっと南のほうです。さすがに山久学園に通うには遠くて"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1825
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_e26f7fcc:

    # li "With her working hours getting longer and Yamaku being so far away, there was little choice in the end but to move into the dormitories."
    li "そのことと、姉さんの仕事時間が長くなったこともあって、最終的に寮に引っ越すしかなくなったんです"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1827
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_d2f8c5a3:

    # "Well, that explains the chatter about cooking. Evidently regaining her composure, she livens back up… at least, in part."
    "なるほど、それで料理の話をしていたのか。どうやらリリーは落ち着きを取り戻したらしく、元気になったようだ……まあ、それなりに。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1832
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_5515bd00:

    # li "I take it you're better rested, now?"
    li "もう体は休まったみたいですね"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1834
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_47b6c948:

    # hi "Sorry?"
    hi "なに？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1839
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_ac56ae52:

    # li "You sound less exhausted than you did when you first came in."
    li "最初に入ってきたときよりも息が落ち着いたようですし"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1841
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_c25e81a7:

    # "To be able to pick out my breathing like that… she must have pretty good ears."
    "俺の呼吸をそんな風に聞き分けられるなんて……リリーの耳はとても良いに違いない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1843
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_aa9d0765:

    # hi "Yeah. Ended up walking all over town, despite only planning on taking a short walk down here."
    hi "ああ。ちょっと散歩するだけのつもりだったのに、結局町中を歩いちゃったよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1845
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_cbf2f67d:

    # "Reminded of my thirst from the walk, I lean forward to take a sip."
    "散歩の話でのどの渇きを思い出し、一口飲むために身を乗り出す。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1849
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_2515ef69:

    # "Without further ado, Lilly starts on her cup of strong-smelling tea."
    "そして、リリーも香りの強い紅茶に口をつけ始める。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1851
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_0c8aaf49:

    # "I guess I'd better get going back to Yamaku. There's only so long I can stall studying for, and I want to get a good night's sleep before the festival."
    "もう学園に戻ったほうがいいかもしれない。いつまでも勉強を後回しにすることはできないし、学園祭の前にはちゃんと寝ておきたい。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1855
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_d6e26891:

    # "Standing from my seat, I take the coffee-stained cup from the table."
    "椅子から立ち上がり、テーブルからコーヒーの染みの付いたカップを取る。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1860
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_eb5d9509:

    # li "You're leaving?"
    li "帰るんですか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1862
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_3e7f2798:

    # hi "Yeah. You going to head back as well? It's getting kind of late."
    hi "うん。リリーも戻る？　時間も遅くなってるし"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1864
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_a8e9bca7:

    # "For a moment she pauses, before lifting her face over her teacup as if she was looking at me."
    "リリーは少し待って、ティーカップの上に身を乗り出す。俺を見ているかのようだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1871
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_21755903:

    # li "Yuuko, could we have one more coffee please?"
    li "優子さん、コーヒーをもう一杯もらえますか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1873
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_d5b22bc4:

    # yu "Okay, I'll bring it right away!"
    yu "いいわよ、すぐもっていくね！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1875
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_4fe11e2e:

    # hi "That's… not subtle."
    hi "わかりやすい……やり方だね"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1880
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_c58fb11a:

    # "She gives a short giggle at my frank assessment of her maneuver. It's surprisingly childish and carefree, given her otherwise collected appearance."
    "リリーはその作戦に対する率直な意見にくすくすと短く笑う。彼女の落ち着いた容姿からすると、それは驚くほど子どもっぽく、屈託がない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1882
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_fb33f394:

    # "In the end, though, I have little reason to refuse. To be honest I can hardly say no, all things considered."
    "まあ、俺には断る理由がほとんどない。正直、どう考えてもノーとは言えない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1884
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_396e3180:

    # "Giving a manufactured sigh, I take a seat opposite her."
    "わざとらしくため息をついて、俺はリリーの向かいの席に座る。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1886
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_51ea9757:

    # hi "Wanting company, then?"
    hi "話し相手が欲しかったの？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1891
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_ef10e7f5:

    # li "Hmm… I'd say that it's more that I was wondering…"
    li "うーん……ちょっと聞きたいことがある、とでもいいますか……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1893
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_c717ac55:

    # "I see she's in questioning mode, again. She does seem to be unusually interested in me, or at least curious."
    "また質問モードに入っているらしい。いつになく俺に興味を持っているみたいだ。さもなければ、好奇心かもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1898
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_260ca9f1:

    # li "Do you have any siblings?"
    li "ご兄弟は何人いらっしゃるんですか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1900
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_717de9c3:

    # "Not exactly an unexpected tangent."
    "そんなに意外な質問でもないな。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1902
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_39f6254f:

    # hi "No, only child. To be honest, the idea of having someone that close makes me a bit envious."
    hi "いや、一人っ子だよ。正直、そんなに近い関係の人がいるってだけでうらやましいよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1907
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_ef05aba7:

    # li "Interesting…"
    li "なるほど……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1909
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_9c6764d8:

    # "I raise an eyebrow, which of course goes unseen. The short silence communicates the question well enough."
    "俺は眉を上げるけど、もちろん見られてはいない。短い沈黙が、俺の問いかけを十分に伝えてくれる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1914
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_dd5f3006:

    # li "It's just that others have said the same thing before."
    li "前にも他の人たちにそう言われたことがあるんですよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1916
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_3e14cfe1:

    # li "It's a difficult subject to try and think about objectively, given that I've always had someone like that."
    li "私のそばにはずっと姉がいたので、客観的に考えてみるのはなかなか難しいですね"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1918
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_869811de:

    # "I can mostly understand what Lilly means, given that it would be hard to place oneself outside of a situation they've been in all their life."
    "リリーの言いたいことは大体理解できる。生まれ育った環境と別の立場に自分を置いてみるのは難しいんだろう。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1920
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_b527e160:

    # "She and her sister must have a pretty close relationship."
    "彼女たち姉妹はかなり仲が良いに違いない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1922
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_3a5aee2b:

    # "Taking pains to interrupt us as little as possible, Yuuko dutifully comes over and places a cup on the table."
    "できるだけ俺たちの邪魔にならないように優子さんがうやうやしくやってきて、テーブルにカップを一つ置く。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1924
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_95103f0c:

    # "Lilly thanks her as I sit back, taking in this vexing girl in front of me."
    "リリーが優子さんにお礼を言うそばで、俺はくつろぎながらこの目の前の一筋縄ではいかない子を眺める。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1926
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_b65fb927:

    # "Despite always seeming to be on her guard and in control of herself when talking to others, she has an almost childlike curiosity about other people."
    "いつも隙がなくて、他人と話すときは理性的に自分をコントロールしてる感じだけど、子どもみたいな好奇心も持っているんだな。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1928
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_f77440aa:

    # "That said, those rare moments she seems to slightly lower her guard are the most insightful into how she thinks."
    "とはいえ、リリーもごくたまに心の内をのぞかせることがある。それは彼女の考え方に迫ることができる絶好のチャンスだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1930
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_406b09fb:

    # "Reaching forward for my drink, I realize something I probably should've noticed earlier."
    "目の前にある自分の飲み物に手を伸ばし、もっと早く気づくべきだったことに気づく。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1932
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_bdc20978:

    # "…I think I'm starting to become kind of curious about her."
    "……俺はリリーのことを知りたいと思い始めている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1941
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_ac022d97:

    # "Despite making a good pace, it's already nightfall by the time I reach the large iron gates in front of the school."
    "かなりのペースだったのに、学校の大きい鉄製の正門に着いた時にはもう日が暮れている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1943
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_621f4c21:

    # "While it's nice to have plenty of time to wander around by virtue of living right next to the school, I can't help but get the feeling that very few students actually take the opportunity."
    "学園のすぐ隣に住むことでぶらぶらできる時間がたっぷりあるのはうれしいけれど、そうできる生徒はほとんどいないんだと感じずにはいられない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1948
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_3267a522:

    # "Compared to the number of students I see milling around on-campus during free time, it's startlingly rare to see anyone around town."
    "空き時間に校内を行き来している生徒の数に比べると、町中では驚くほど人を見かけない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1950
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_ff3831dd:

    # "Given the large number of accommodations and facilities that the school offers, many of them might simply not see any point in venturing outside, let alone people such as Hanako and Kenji."
    "学園にあるかなりの数の宿泊設備と施設を考えると、多くの生徒は外に出ること自体にあまり意味を感じないのかもしれない。まして、華子や健二みたいなタイプは言うまでもない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1952
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_d6894daa:

    # "It makes me wonder if students like Shizune, Misha, and Lilly are the exception for this school, rather than the norm."
    "そう考えると、静音やミーシャ、リリーのような生徒はこの学校ではむしろ例外なのだろうか。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1958
translate jp a1_saturday_sip_p2_cb597914:

    # "As I wander back to my dorm room, I continue to compare my old school with Yamaku. As I do so, I begin to be surprised that I managed to get even this used to everything that's happened to me."
    "寮の部屋にぶらりと戻りながら、俺は前の学校と山久学園を比べ続ける。そうするほどに、これまでに起こったいろんなことにここまで慣れてしまった自分に驚く。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1979
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_377d2cc4:

    # "At five minutes past eight, an unbelievably loud banging jolts me awake. It's coming from outside my door."
    "８時５分過ぎ、バンバンと何かを叩く音が聞こえてくる。信じられないくらい大きな音に俺は飛び起きてしまう。ドアの外からだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1988
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_1a88da30:

    # "Quickly, I open the door to see Shizune and Misha standing side-by-side before me. Both of them look a little worn out, although it's more noticeable on Misha."
    "すぐにドアを開けると、静音とミーシャが目の前に並んでいる。二人とも少し疲れているように見える。ミーシャのくたびれ具合の方が目立っているけど。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1990
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_da83c19e:

    # hi "Which one of you knocked?"
    hi "今ノックしたのはどっちだよ？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1992
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_9dd44795:

    # "I ask, echoing the question that must be on the mind of everyone in the entire building."
    "建物の中にいる人全員が思ったであろう問いを、俺は尋ねる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1997
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_5aeece62:

    # mi "Ahahaha, that's not important, Hicchan!"
    mi "あははは、そんなのどうでもいいじゃん、ひっちゃん！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:1999
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_164ce49d:

    # "She quickly dismisses it without even batting an eye."
    "ミーシャは顔色ひとつ変えず、あっけなくスルーする。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2004
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_a10ed61c:

    # mi "Oh? You're still in your pajamas, Hicchan? So you don't wake up at eight?"
    mi "あれぇ？　ひっちゃん、まだパジャマ着てるの？　もう８時なのに起きないんだ？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2006
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_2b72c85a:

    # "I notice her hair is wet. Her curls are barely holding their shape."
    "ミーシャの髪が湿っているのに気づく。あの巻き髪もかろうじて形を保っている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2008
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_a77b85eb:

    # hi "No, I thought I'd sleep a bit later since it's the weekend and all, and I've been seriously sleep-deprived this week."
    hi "まあな。せっかくの週末だし、少しゆっくり寝ようと思ってたんだ。今週はマジで睡眠不足だったし"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2010
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_c662b41d:

    # "I wonder if she missed the poison in my words."
    "今の皮肉はちゃんと通じただろうか。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2015
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2020
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_82233c16:

    # mi "Then it's a good thing we came to wake you up!"
    mi "じゃあちょうどいいわ！　わたしたち、起こしに来てあげたんだから！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2025
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2030
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_6a268392:

    # mi "Anyway, Hicchan, I guess you would like to know why we're here, wouldn't you?"
    mi "それはおいといて、ひっちゃん、どうしてわたしたちがここに来てるのか、知りたくない？"

