translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_ef2b123c_31:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2700
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_ac1e051c:

    # mi "Now all that's left is the stakes! What the winner wins, or, more interestingly, what the loser loses!"
    mi "じゃああとは何を賭けるか決めるだけね！　勝ったほうの賞品と、いいえ、もっと面白いのは負けたほうの罰！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2702
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_d5322af5:

    # hi "Hey!"
    hi "おい！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2704
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_cbe22af3:

    # "This is a very dangerous game I'm playing. Shizune herself is a very dangerous girl, if she can only think in terms of winning and losing."
    "これはとてもヤバい勝負だ。静音がそもそもヤバい。こいつが勝ち負けでしか物事を考えないのだとすれば。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2706
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_396f2729:

    # "If she views every time that I talk with her as some kind of battle of wills, I don't think I could take it."
    "俺と話すたびに静音がそれを勝負扱いするのでは、俺は耐えられそうにない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2708
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_91a89c00:

    # "That kind of thing drives people insane. She's too Machiavellian; before this I'd assumed she was just kind of stoic."
    "そういう風にされては頭がおかしくなる。静音は目的のために手段を選ばなさすぎるんだ。今までは、単に冷静なだけだと思っていたけど。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2710
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_94c2501b:

    # "But nevertheless, I'm interested. In hindsight, I realize that I just challenged her to what is essentially a duel without any rules that won't end until one of us… what?"
    "それでもなお、俺は興味を引かれている。考えてみれば、俺は静音になんのルールもない勝負を挑んでいたんだ、と気づく。 終わるのは俺たちのうちどちらかが……どうなるんだ？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2712
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_8d970ea7:

    # "I guess that's it. That's so vague. What are the conditions for winning or losing? The first person to feel stupid loses?"
    "つまりそういうことか。そこがあまりに曖昧なんだ。勝ち負けの条件はなんだ？　最初に恥をかいたほうが負けなのか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2714
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_ae6464e4:

    # hi "I don't know, I've never had to think of anything like this before."
    hi "どうだろうな。そんなの考えたことは今まで一度もないんだけど"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2719
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_8baf874b:

    # mi "Never?"
    mi "一度も？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2721
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_649932a8:

    # hi "Never."
    hi "一度も"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2726
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_3d1635fa:

    # mi "So you have never gambled, Hicchan?"
    mi "じゃあひっちゃんは一度も賭けをしたことがないってこと？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2728
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_35448c07:

    # hi "I'm surprised you two have."
    hi "二人ともやったことあるのかよ。そっちのほうがびっくりだよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2733
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_ef2b123c_32:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2738
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_f47fe86a:

    # mi "Oh, come on… It's just for fun, anyway! Between friends~!"
    mi "もう、固いこと言わないの……ただの遊びなんだから！　友達同士の～！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2743
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_ee9f7d68:

    # mi "It's about causing humiliation, suffering, and absolute despair! Isn't that the point?"
    mi "恥をかかせて苦しめて絶対的な絶望を与えるのが目的なんだから！　そういうことじゃない？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2745
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_8b580b5e:

    # "Shizune puts a finger to her temple thoughtfully."
    "静音は思慮深げにこめかみに指を当てる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2750
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_b33ba1f7:

    # shi "…!"
    shi "……！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2755
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_cf5bf557:

    # mi "Hm… Ah, how about this, Hicchan: if you lose, you have to go to school one day without any pants on."
    mi "うーん……あ、じゃあこういうのはどうかな。ひっちゃんが負けたら、一日ズボンはかずにパンツ一丁で学校に行くの"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2757
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_3ea62a08:

    # hi "Are you insane?"
    hi "お前ら正気か？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2759
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_01ff08f1:

    # "Although in comparison to what I was afraid she would say, it's pretty mild."
    "こいつらが何を言い出すかと恐れていたことに比べれば、ずいぶんおとなしいけど。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2761
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_ca235321:

    # hi "Can't we just bet money, like normal people?"
    hi "普通の人みたいにお金をかけるんじゃダメなのか？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2766
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_ef2b123c_33:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2771
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_27b067ff:

    # mi "It's not like you could match my wager if we did~! Now, it's your turn! …But nothing perverted! Understand?"
    mi "ほんとにお金賭けたら、わたしの掛け金に合わせられるわけないでしょ～！　さあ、そっちの番よ！　……でもえっちな条件は禁止だからね！　わかった？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2776
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_352a2cb7_2:

    # mi "Hahaha!"
    mi "ははは！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2778
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_85144872:

    # hi "I think I need more time."
    hi "ちょっと時間をくれ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2780
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_b2482000:

    # "This is going to have me constantly on edge for weeks."
    "これじゃ、俺は何週間も追い詰められっぱなしになるぞ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2785
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_efbabf07:

    # mi "Okay~! Come on, you should both hurry up, your drinks are getting cold!"
    mi "おっけ～！　ほら、二人とも急ごうよ、飲み物が冷めちゃうよ！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2790
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_8275aa5e:

    # "I quickly down the rest of my coffee as Shizune does the same, staring at me with a fierce look of competition in her eyes."
    "俺はコーヒーの残りをさっさと飲む。静音も俺を激しい競争心に満ちた目で見つめながら、同じように飲む。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2792
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_95396eba:

    # "It seems like a waste for her to be gulping down something that someone may have died for her to enjoy."
    "誰かが命を落としたかもしれないお茶をそんなにあっさり飲んでしまうのは、なんだかもったいない気がする。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2797
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_f2bd33a4:

    # mi "Hicchan, are you sure you don't want to hang out tomorrow? A lot of people are looking forward to it; you don't want to miss out."
    mi "ひっちゃん、ほんとに明日わたしたちと一緒にでかけたくないの？　楽しみにしてる人はたくさんいるんだから。ひっちゃんだって行ったほうがいいよ"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2799
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_fcf55c9b:

    # "I mumble unintelligibly at her."
    "俺は言葉にならないつぶやきをぼそぼそという。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2804
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_358f8746:

    # mi "I don't really understand…"
    mi "何言ってるのかわかんないよ……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2806
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_c7b2b6b1:

    # "It's time to think. Shizune's drink is smaller, but I can consume mine faster."
    "今は考えるときだ。静音の飲み物は俺のより少ないが、それでも俺は静音よりも速く飲みきれる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2808
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_08d0b319:

    # "If Shizune finishes her drink first, she might skip out on paying, leaving me to pick up the tab, even though she said the drinks were on her."
    "静音が先に飲みきったら、自分がおごるといったのにもかかわらず、会計を済ませずに俺に払いを押しつけて逃げるかもしれない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2810
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_a7af260b:

    # "Because I have no money on me, I would be humiliated, and therefore this could be considered a loss."
    "俺はまったくお金の持ち合わせがないので、恥をかくことになる。これは負けと見なされるだろう。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2812
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_bc670915:

    # "If I finish first, the laws of chivalry would make me look like a jerk, as I would need to run out of this teahouse, leaving her to pay for everything. That could also be considered a loss. She would use that."
    "俺が先に飲み終わってしまったら、俺はお茶屋から逃げ出して払いを静音に押しつけなくてはならない。そして騎士道精神に照らして俺はバカ野郎扱いされる。 これも負けと見なされるだろう。静音ならそうするに違いない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2814
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_e54a8735:

    # "In the event of a draw, she may attempt to run out the door, and I'll probably do the same. This might lead to a collision at the door, which would be humiliating, but not overly so. …And Misha would be left to pick up the tab."
    "引き分けの場合、静音はドアに向けて走り出すかもしれない。俺もそうするだろう。そしてドアの手前で正面衝突。屈辱ではあるけどそれほどではない……代金はミーシャが払うことになる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2816
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_679f04c4:

    # "This is really childish. I'm a little disappointed in Shizune, and myself."
    "まるでガキみたいじゃないか。俺は静音と、そして俺自身に失望する。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2821
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_506b1101:

    # mi "Well, Hicchan, it'd be really nice if we could all celebrate how well we put everything together for the festival by taking a look at our handiwork…"
    mi "ねえひっちゃん、わたしたちが学園祭のためにがんばって作り上げたものを見て回って、よくやったねって言えたら、とってもすてきだと思うの……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2823
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_0a3ca316:

    # "Misha seems oblivious to the fact that an epic battle of wills is raging in front of her. I nod slowly and down the last of my coffee."
    "自分の目の前で壮大な戦いが繰り広げられているという事実に、ミーシャはまったく気づいていないようだ。俺はゆっくりとうなずき、最後のコーヒーを飲み下す。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2825
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_20e37104:

    # hi "Well, I am finished enjoying my drink. I guess it's time for me to leave. And I am going to leave now. Calmly."
    hi "さて、俺は飲み終わったぞ。じゃあ俺はもう帰らなきゃ。ほんとに今すぐ帰るから。ゆっくりな"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2830
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_ef2b123c_34:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2835
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_bb9a2687:

    # mi "You too, Shicchan?"
    mi "しっちゃんも帰るの？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2837
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_0448e691:

    # mi "Why are you two acting so weird?"
    mi "二人ともなんか変だよ、どうしたの？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2842
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_90b768b1:

    # "I quickly walk out the door and Shizune follows. Misha is going to have to foot the bill."
    "俺は素早くドアへと歩き、静音も続く。会計はミーシャが払うはめになるけど。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2847
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_7bc2efd0:

    # "Sorry, Misha."
    "すまん、ミーシャ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2852
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_1549a0b3:

    # "Catching up to me, Shizune quickly pushes her glasses up and presses a note into my hand."
    "俺に追いついた静音が、さっと眼鏡を押し上げて、紙切れを俺の手に突っ込む。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2856
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_a9e1c92e:

    # hi "So you think you can win today? That's kind of cocky, Shizune."
    hi "お前、今日は俺に勝てると思ってるんだろ？　ちょっと調子に乗ってないか、静音"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2858
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_009a3712:

    # "I forgot for a second that she can't hear me. I nod."
    "俺の返事が静音には聞こえない、ということを一瞬忘れていた。俺はうなずく。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2860
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_ed7b0b00:

    # "Right now, she seems much cuter than she usually is, smiling softly with a hint of confidence coming through."
    "今この瞬間、ほのかな自信をのぞかせながら微笑んでいる静音は、普段よりもずっとかわいらしく見える。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2862
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_34f4304f:

    # "Shizune looks energetic and carefree, although it could just be the caffeine."
    "静音は活発で気ままに見える。カフェインのせいかもしれないけど。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2867
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_e661b2f4:

    # "She winks, and extends her hand for a handshake. I wonder if there's a buzzer in there and she plans to shock me, but that doesn't seem like something she would do, so I accept."
    "静音はウインクし、握手するために手を伸ばす。手にスタンガンを隠し持って俺をしびれさせるつもりじゃないか、と一瞬考える。でもそんなのは静音らしくないので、俺はその手を握る。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2869
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_cad72ff7:

    # "With a squeeze, she pushes another note into my hand. I momentarily think that it's a buzzer and wonder if the shock could kill me."
    "手を握ると、静音はまたメモを俺の手に押し込む。瞬間、それがスタンガンで、俺はショックで死ぬんじゃないか、という考えが脳裏に走る。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2874
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_ad85ad8c:

    # "Shizune smirks and then runs off."
    "静音はにやりと笑い、走り去る。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2878
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_d2dd9340:

    # "I crush the note in my fist dramatically, but no one is there to see it, and that makes me sad."
    "俺は芝居がかった仕草でメモを握りつぶす。でも誰もそれを見てはいなくて、俺は悲しくなる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2880
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_4c65841b:

    # "I wonder if it's too late to go back to the shop and ask Misha for directions."
    "店に戻ってミーシャに帰り道を聞くにはもう遅いだろうか、と考える。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2882
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_a6c79841:

    # "But then again, I gave her a hard time for not knowing the way here, so I can't allow her to score off me for not knowing the way back."
    "でも行きの道順を知らないためにミーシャには苦労をかけた。帰り道を知らないからといって、ミーシャに借りを作るわけにはいかない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2884
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_985876df:

    # "And if I ask her, Shizune could see it as a victory. No, it's not necessary."
    "それにミーシャに道を聞いてしまったら、静音はそれを勝ちと見なすかもしれない。だめだ。道案内なしでもいける。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2888
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_7a2476aa:

    # "The school is on top of a damn hill, how hard could it be to find?"
    "学校はあのいまいましい丘のてっぺんにある。あそこに行くなんて楽勝だろう？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2890
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_f3a142b4:

    # "I may be slightly directionally challenged, but I'm sure that even I can do this."
    "俺はちょっとばかり方向感覚が不自由かもしれないけど、このくらい俺にだってできるに決まってる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2897
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_552f44b9:

    # "About an hour and a half later, I walk the long paved path leading from the gates to the main building."
    "約一時間半後、俺は校門から本校舎までの舗装された道を歩いている。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2904
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_283abbba:

    # mi "Hahaa! Just the person we were waiting for. So you made it here eventually, Hicchan, good! Now it's time for work work work~!"
    mi "ははあ！　もう待ちくたびれたよ。やっと戻ってきたんだね、ひっちゃん。よろしい！　さあ仕事の時間だよ、仕事仕事～！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2906
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_cef1c1c0:

    # "Misha and Shizune had laid an ambush for me in the main lobby of the ground floor and I walked straight into it. I should have just circled around the school like I had originally planned, but I thought that I was overreacting and being silly."
    "ミーシャと静音は１階のロビーで俺を待ちかまえていて、俺はまっすぐそこに飛び込んでしまった。 最初に考えていたとおり、校舎を迂回すれば良かったのだけど、そこまでするのも考えすぎだしばかばかしい、と思っていた。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2908
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_eb0a3e40:

    # "Misha is waving a thick stack of printouts in my general direction, taunting me."
    "ミーシャは分厚いプリントの束を俺のほうにパタパタ振って、俺を挑発する。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2913
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_36548c8e:

    # mi "We sort of need your help~!"
    mi "手伝ってほしいかな～！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2915
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_9decffaf:

    # hi "Sort of?"
    hi "かな？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2920
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_32516b35:

    # mi "We need your help~!"
    mi "手伝ってほしいの～！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2925
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_ef2b123c_35:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2930
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_0cfc601b:

    # mi "You will help us!"
    mi "手伝うのよ！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2932
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_491915a5:

    # "Misha speaks with her usual playful, carefree manner, but even so I can hear Shizune's unnervingly hard severity behind it."
    "ミーシャはいつもの陽気でのんきそうな口調で話す。それでも静音のどきっとするような強烈な厳しさは伝わってくる。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2934
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_2cc172ce:

    # hi "That sounds like an order."
    hi "命令みたいに聞こえるな"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2936
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_f2e15bc9:

    # mi "Really? Is it?"
    mi "ほんとに？　そうなの？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2941
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_ef2b123c_36:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2946
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_5f735d25:

    # mi "Eh? It is?"
    mi "え？　そうなんだ？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2951
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_04201dd8:

    # mi "Ah, sorry, Hicchan, I guess it is! Hahahaha!"
    mi "あー、ごめんひっちゃん、ほんとにそうみたい！　はははは！"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:2953
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_5024b03d:

    # "She doesn't sound very sorry at all."
