# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3352
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_b7a6c607:

    # "I turn immediately to Shizune, who gives me a curt wave and a surprisingly cheery smile before quickly vanishing out the door."
    "俺はすぐさま静音に振り向く。静音は素っ気なく手をひらひらと振りながら、驚くほど明るい笑顔を見せると、あっという間にドアの向こうに姿を消す。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3361
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_490e7b40:

    # "Well then why didn't you just say you wanted to take a break!?"
    "じゃあどうして素直に休憩したいって言わないんだよ！？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3363
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_40621341:

    # "I used to think that Shizune and Misha were polar opposites. Misha always seems so energetic and playful, like any other girl. Shizune, on the other hand, always seemed distant. Aggressively manipulative and vaguely scary, but distant."
    "今まで静音とミーシャは両極端ってくらい違うと思っていた。ミーシャは普通の女の子と同じようにいつも元気でお茶目。一方静音はいつも冷たい感じがした。 強引なまでに仕切りたがりで、なんとなく怖いけど、でもそんな感じだった。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3365
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_b0682ddb:

    # "There were times when I thought that she had no sense of humor. As cute as she was, I'd almost never seen her smile. Not to mention all the other things."
    "静音には全く冗談が通じないんじゃないか、と思うことも何度かあった。 あいつはかわいいけど、笑ってるところはほとんど見たことがない。その他もろもろの仕草は言うまでもない。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3367
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_5a7dc654:

    # "The analytical stare, the permanently stoic expression, and even her penmanship; so mechanically precise that everything she writes looks typed."
    "あの分析するような視線、いつも変わらず冷静な表情、それにあの筆跡だってそうだ。静音の書く字はいつも機械のようにきっちりしている。まるで活字みたいだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3369
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_68002b6a:

    # "But Shizune and Misha really aren't as different as I'd thought."
    "でも静音とミーシャは、俺が思っていたほど違っているわけじゃないんだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3371
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_8f54404a:

    # hi "I'm a little surprised."
    hi "ちょっと驚いたな"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3378
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_12d0300f:

    # mi "Why?"
    mi "どうして？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3380
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_5839b852:

    # hi "Shizune. I didn't know that she liked to joke around like that."
    hi "静音がさ。ああいう風に冗談かますやつだとは知らなかったから"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3382
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_ff7d4db8:

    # "What I mean to say is, I didn't know that she could act so girlish. It was actually pretty cute."
    "俺が言いたかったのは、あいつがあんなに女の子らしいことができるとは知らなかった、ってことだ。正直、あれはマジでかわいかった。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3387
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_79e1c8a4:

    # mi "You would be surprised, Hicchan."
    mi "まあ驚くよね、ひっちゃん"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3389
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_5d2e01f8:

    # hi "Well, I didn't know you and her were so close, either, the first time I saw you."
    hi "最初にお前に会ったときだって、お前と静音がこんなに似てるとは知らなかったしな"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3391
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_bfa2ec07:

    # "I've always been curious as to how these two met."
    "この二人がどうやって巡り会ったのかは前から知りたかったんだ。"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3393
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_dc487c2b:

    # hi "Do you two go far back or something?"
    hi "二人とも昔から知り合いだったりするの？"

# game/script-a1-saturday.rpy:3395
translate jp a1_saturday_shanghaied_5e4b9123:

